var book = {
	"name": "2 Berɛsosɛm",
	"numChapters": 36,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Dawid ba Salomo hyɛɛ ne ho den n’ahennie ho, na AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn dii n’akyi na ɔmaa no so kɛseɛ pa ara.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Salomo kasa kyerɛɛ Israelfoɔ nyinaa, mpem mpem ne ɔha ha so asafohene ne atemmufoɔ ne Israel nyinaa so mmapɔmma a wɔyɛ agyanom atitire no nyinaa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Salomo ne badwa a wɔka ne ho no nyinaa sii mu kɔɔ sorɔnsorɔnbea a ɛwɔ Gibeon no. Ɛhɔ na na Nyankopɔn ahyiaeɛ ntomadan a AWURADE akoa Mose yɛɛ no ɛserɛ soɔ no wɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> (Nanso Nyankopɔn adaka no deɛ, Dawid kɔfa firii Kiriat-yearim de baa deɛ Dawid siesie maa no no, na wasi ntomadan ama no wɔ Yerusalem.)",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na kɔbere mfrafraeɛ afɔrebukyia a Hur ba Uri ba Besalel yɛeɛ no si AWURADE tenabea no anim hɔ, na Salomo ne badwa no kɔhwehwɛɛ AWURADE akyiri kwan.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Salomo bɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ wɔ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ afɔrebukyia a ɛsi AWURADE anim ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no anim no so, na ɔbɔɔ so ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ apem.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Anadwo no ara na Onyankopɔn yii ne ho adi kyerɛɛ Salomo, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Srɛ deɛ memma woɔ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛnna Salomo ka kyerɛɛ Onyankopɔn sɛ: Wo na woyɛɛ m’agya Dawid adɔeɛ kɛseɛ, na woayɛ me ɔhene asi n’ananmu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Afei, AWURADE Nyankopɔn, ma w’asɛm ntim mma m’agya Dawid. Na wo na woasi me hene, ɔman a wɔdɔɔso sɛ asase so mfuturo soɔ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ma me nyansa ne nimdeɛ na memfiri adi ɔman yi anim na memmra mu, na hwan na ɔbɛbu wo man kɛseɛ yi atɛn?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Onyankopɔn ka kyerɛɛ Salomo sɛ: Ɛsiane sɛ yei wɔ w’akoma mu, na woammisa ahonya, akoradeɛ ne animuonyam ne w’atamfo nkwa, na nna dodoɔ nso woammisa, na mmom woabisa nyansa ne nimdeɛ, sɛ wode bɛbu me man a mayɛ wo wɔn so hene no atɛn yi,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> nyansa ne nimdeɛ no, wɔde ama wo na ahonya ne akoradeɛ ne animuonyam nso, mɛma wo, a ahemfo a wɔdii w’anim no nnyaa saa da, na w’akyi nso wɔrennya saa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ɛnna Salomo firi sorɔnsorɔnbea a ɛwɔ Gibeon no ne ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no anim baa Yerusalem, na ɔdii Israel so hene.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Salomo boaboaa nteaseɛnam ne apɔnkɔsotefoɔ ano, na ɔnyaa nteaseɛnam apem ahanan ne apɔnkɔsotefoɔ mpemdumienu, na ɔde wɔn duaa nteaseɛnam nkuro mu ne ɔhene nkyɛn Yerusalem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔhene maa dwetɛ ne sika yɛɛ sɛ aboɔ wɔ Yerusalem, na ntweneduro nso ɔmaa ne dodoɔ yɛɛ sɛ akyee a ɛwowɔ mpaperɛ soɔ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wɔkra Salomo apɔnkɔ no firi Misraim ne Kue. Kue na na ɔhene adwadifoɔ no tɔ wɔn tua ka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wɔde teaseɛnam a ne boɔ yɛ dwetɛ nnwetɛbena ahansia ne ɔpɔnkɔ nso a ne boɔ yɛ ɔha aduonum firi Misraim ba. Na saa na na wɔkra bi ma Hetifoɔ ahemfo nyinaa ne Siria ahemfo."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Salomo bɔɔ ne tirim sɛ, ɔbɛsi efie ama AWURADE din, ne n’ahennie.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Salomo kann nnesoafoɔ mpemaduɔson ne bepɔ so abopaefoɔ mpemaduɔwɔtwe ne wɔn so ahwɛfoɔ mpensa ahansia.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Salomo soma maa wɔkɔɔ Tirohene Huram nkyɛn sɛ: Sɛdeɛ wo ne m’agya Dawid yɛeɛ, na wobrɛɛ no tweneduro nnua, na ɔde sii ne fie tenaa mu no,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> hwɛ, me nso merebɛsi efie mama AWURADE me Nyankopɔn din, na ayɛ kronkron ama no, na wɔahye aduhwam a ɛyɛ hwam n’anim, na wɔasiesie kyerɛ paanoo daa, na wɔabɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ daa anɔpa ne anwummerɛ ne home nna ne abosome foforɔ ne AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn afahyɛ ase. Yei ne Israel amanneɛ de kɔsi daa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na efie a merebɛsie no so, ɛfiri sɛ yɛn Nyankopɔn no so sene anyame nyinaa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na hwan mpo na ɔbɛtumi asi efie ama no? Na ɔsoro ne ɔsoro mu soro rentumi nkora no, na hwan ne me, sɛ mɛsi efie mama no, gye aduhwam a wɔhye no n’anim?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na afei soma ɔbarima nyansafoɔ bi brɛ me, na ɔmmɛdi sika, dwetɛ, kɔbere mfrafraeɛ, dadeɛ, ntoma a ɛberedum, koogyan ne bibire mu adwini, na ɔnim nnua mu nsemayie nso, na ɔnka adwumfoɔ a wɔwɔ me nkyɛn Yuda ne Yerusalem a m’agya Dawid asiesie wɔn asie no ho.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nanso brɛ me ntweneduro ne pepeaa ne abako nnua firi Lebanon, na menim sɛ wo nkoa nim Lebanon nnua twa, na hwɛ, me nkoa bɛka wo nkoa ho.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔnsiesie nnua pii pa mma me, na efie a merebɛsie no so na ɛyɛ nwanwa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na hwɛ wo nkoa nnuapaefoɔ no mɛma wɔn ayuo susukoraa mpemaduonu ne atokoɔ susukoraa mpemaduonu ne nsa galɔn ɔpeha du ne ngo galɔn ɔpeha du.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnna Tirohene Huram twerɛɛ nwoma brɛɛ Salomo sɛ: Ɔdɔ a AWURADE dɔ ne man nti na ɔde wo asi wɔn so hene.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Huram kaa sɛ: Nhyira ne AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn a ɔyɛɛ ɔsoro ne asase no, sɛ wama Ɔhene Dawid ɔba nyansafoɔ a ɔnim de ne nhunumu a ɔbɛsi efie ama AWURADE, ne n’ahemfie.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na afei masoma ɔbarima nyansafoɔ a ɔwɔ nhunumu a ɔne Huram-Abi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɔyɛ ɔbaa bi a ɔfiri Dan mmammaa mu ba, na n’agya yɛ Tironi. Ɔnim sika ne dwetɛ, kɔbere mfrafraeɛ, dadeɛ, aboɔ ne nnua, ntoma a ɛbere dum, bibire ne nwera ne koogyan mu adwinni, na ɔnim nsema ahodoɔ nyinaa nso, na ɔbɛtumi adi adwini biara a wɔbɛhwehwɛ no ne hɔ, sɛ ɔmmɛka w’anyansadwumfoɔ ne me wura Dawid w’agya no, anyansadwumfoɔ ho.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na afei, ayuo ne atokoɔ ne ngo ne nsa a me wura kaeɛ no, ɔmfa mmrɛ ne nkoa no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na yɛn deɛ, yɛbɛbu nnua afiri Lebanon sɛdeɛ ɛhia woɔ nyinaa, na yɛde ayɛ mpuna de abrɛ wo, Yopa po so, na wo nso wode aforo akɔ Yerusalem.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Salomo kanee mmarima ahɔhoɔ a wɔwɔ Israel asase soɔ no, ɔkan a n’agya kanee wɔn no akyi, na wɔhunuu wɔn sɛ wɔyɛ mpemha aduonum mmiɛnsa ne ahansia.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ wɔn mu mpemaduɔson nnesoafoɔ ne bepɔ so abopaefoɔ mpemaduɔwɔtwe ne ahwɛfoɔ mpensa ahansia, sɛ wɔmma nkurɔfoɔ no nyɛ adwuma."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Salomo firii aseɛ sii AWURADE fie no wɔ Yerusalem, Moria bepɔ a wɔkyerɛɛ n’agya Dawid no so, faako a Dawid hyɛeɛ, Yebusini Ornan ayuporebea hɔ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔfirii aseɛ sii no bosome a ɛtɔ so mmienu, n’ahennie afe a ɛtɔ so nnan mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na yei ne fapem a Salomo too sɛ ɔde resi AWURADE dan no: Ne ntwemu yɛ akane nsusuiɛ no mu basafa aduasa, na ne trɛ nso basafa du.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ntwonoowa a ɛwɔ ɛdan no trɛ anim no, ne ntwemu yɛ basafa du, na ne korɔn, basafa aduosia. Na ɔde sika amapa duraa emu fam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɛdan kɛseɛ no, ɔde pepeaa nnua kataa ho, na ɔde sika pa kataa ho, na ɔdii so adwini, mmɛ ne ntweaban.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔde aboɔ a ne boɔ yɛ den duraa ɛdan no ho sɛ ahyehyɛdeɛ. Na sika no yɛ Parwaim sika.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔde sika kataa ɛdan no mpuna, aponnwa, n’afasuo ne n’apono ntanta no ho. Na ɔsenee kerubim guguu afasuo no ho.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ kronkronkronbea dan no, ne ntwemu sɛdeɛ ɛdan no trɛ teɛ yɛ basafa du, na ne trɛ yɛ basafa du, na ɔde sika pa a ano si talente ahansia kataa ho.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na deɛ wɔkari de yɛɛ nnadewa no ano si sika nnwetɛbena aduonum. Na ɔsoro adan no nso, ɔde sika kataa ho.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na kronkron mu kronkronbea dan no mu no, ɔde dua senee kerubim mmienu, na ɔde sika duraa ho.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na kerubim no ntaban ntwemu yɛ basafa du, baako ataban baako yɛ basafa mmienu ne fa, na ɛka ɛdan no fasuo, ataban baako no nso yɛ basafa mmienu ne fa na ɛka kerub baako no ataban.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na kerub baako no nso ataban yɛ basafa mmienu ne fa, na ɛka ɛdan no fasuo no, na ataban baako no nso yɛ basafa mmienu ne fa, na ɛpem kerub baako no ataban no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kerubim yi ntaban a wɔatrɛ mu no yɛ basafa du, na wɔgyinagyina wɔn nan so, na wɔn anim hwɛ ɛdan no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔde bibire ne asaawa a ɛberedum ne koogyan ne nwera yɛɛ ntwamutam, na ɔyeyɛɛ mu kerubim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ ɛdan no anim adum mmienu, n’atentene, basafa dunson ne fa, na aduntire a ɛwɔ atifi no basafa mmienu ne fa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ ntweaban mpiakyire mu, na ɔde sensɛnee adum no atifi, na ɔyɛɛ atoaa aba nsɛsoɔ, ɔha, hyehyɛɛ ntweaban no mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔmemaa adum no so sisii asɔredan no anim, baako wɔ nifa, na baako wɔ benkum. Na ɔtoo nifa fam deɛ no din: Yakin, na benkum fam deɛ no, ɔtoo no din: Boas."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ afɔrebukyia, ne ntwemu, basafa du, na ne trɛ, basafa du, na ne korɔn, basafa nnum.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ dwaresɛn no kurukuruwa. Ɛfiri ano kɔsi ano yɛ basafa nnum. Na basafa mmienu ne fa ne ne korɔn, na basafa dunum homa twa ho hyia.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ntoa nsɛsoɔ wowɔ aseɛ de twa ɛho nyinaa hyia, edu wɔ anammɔn baako ne fa mu, ɛbɔ no ho kɔntɔnkrɔn; ntoa akyerɛpɛn mmienu, wɔguu no sɛdeɛ aka no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛsi anantwie dummienu so, mmiɛnsa hwɛ atifi fam, na mmiɛnsa hwɛ atɔeɛ, na mmiɛnsa hwɛ anafoɔ fam, na mmiɛnsa hwɛ apueeɛ. Na ɛpo no si wɔn so ɔsoro, na wɔn akyiri nyinaa wɔ emu fam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ne pipiripie yɛ nsayam trɛ, na ɔyɛɛ ano sɛ kuruwa ano, te sɛ sukooko nhwiren a ahane, na galɔn mpem dunum kɔ mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ nnwaresɛn du, na ɔde nnum sisii nifa fam, na ɔde nnum nso sisii atifi fam, sɛ wɔnhohoro nnoɔma ho wɔ mu; ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ nnoɔma no na wɔhohoro ho wɔ mu; na ɛpo no deɛ, ɛwɔ hɔ ma asɔfoɔ, na wɔahohoro wɔn ho wɔ mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ sika nkaneadua du sɛdeɛ ne yɛbea teɛ, na ɔde sisii asɔredan no mu, enum wɔ anafoɔ fam, na enum nso wɔ atifi fam.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ apono du de sisii asɔredan no mu, enum wɔ nifa, na enum wɔ benkum. Na ɔyɛɛ sika nkoraa ɔha.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ asɔfoɔ abannwa ne ban mu adihɔ kɛseɛ no, na ɔde apono sisii adihɔ no ano, na ɔde kɔbere mfrafraeɛ duraa apono no ho.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔde ɛpo no sii atɔeɛ fa a ɛkyerɛ apueeɛ no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Huram yɛɛ nsenaa ne sesa adeɛ ne nkoraa no nso. Na Huram wiee adwuma a ɔyɛ maa Ɔhene Salomo Nyankopɔn fie no yɛ,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> adum mmienu no ne apɔ no ne adum no atifi aduntire mmienu no, ne ntentan mmienu a wɔde kataa adum no atifi ntaasotire apɔ mmienu no ho no,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ne ntentan mmienu no akutuo ahanan, akutuo kyerɛpɛn mmienu yɛ ntentan baako deɛ, sɛ ɛnkata adum no so ntaasotire mmienu apɔ no ho;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na ɔyɛɛ nsugyeɛ nnaka no, na ɔyɛɛ nnyinasoɔ nnaka no so nnwaresɛn no;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ɛpo baako ne aseɛ anantwie dummienu no,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ne nsenaa ne sesa adeɛ ne adinam no ne ɛho nnoɔma nyinaa, Huram-Abi yɛ maa Ɔhene Salomo maa AWURADE fie no, ɛyɛ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ a wɔabere ho hyɛnhyɛn.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Yordan ho mpaperɛ so na ɔhene guu no, dɔteɛ a ɛsɔ mu, Sukot ne Sereda ntam.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Salomo yɛɛ nnoɔma yi nyinaa bebree pa ara, na wɔnnim kɔbere mfrafraeɛ no nkariiɛ ano.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Salomo yɛɛ Nyankopɔn fie nnoɔma no nyinaa ne sika afɔrebukyia no ne apono a kyerɛ paanoo sisi soɔ no",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ne nkaneadua no ne ɛho nkanea a wɔsɔ no, sɛdeɛ ne yɛbea teɛ mpiakyire no anim no, ɛyɛ sika amapa,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na ɛho nhwiren ne nkanea ne adaban no yɛ sika, ne nyinaa yɛ sika ara nko.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na adumgya, nkoraa, aduhwam nkukuwa ne nsramma kukuwa no nso yɛ sika amapa kronkron, na ɛdan no ano apono a ɛwɔ emu fam kronkronkronbea ho no ne asɔrefie dan no apono no yɛ sika."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wɔwiee adwuma a Salomo yɛ maa AWURADE fie no nyinaa. Na Salomo de n’agya Dawid akronkronneɛ no bae, na ɔde dwetɛ ne sika ne nnwinneɛ no nyinaa bɛsiee Nyankopɔn fie akoradeɛ no mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɛnna Salomo boaa Israel mpanimfoɔ ne mmusuakuo no atitire ne Israelfoɔ mu agyanom mmapɔmma no ano bɛhyiaa Yerusalem, sɛ wɔrekɔfa AWURADE apam adaka no afiri Dawid kuro a ɛne Sion no mu aba.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Israel mmarima nyinaa boaboaa wɔn ano baa ɔhene nkyɛn afahyɛ a ɛwɔ nnapɔnna a ɛne bosome a ɛtɔ so nson no mu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Israel mpanimfoɔ nyinaa bae. Na Lewifoɔ no bɛsoaa adaka no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔfaa adaka no ne ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ne akronkronneɛ a ɛwɔ ntomadan no mu nyinaa bae; Lewifoɔ asɔfoɔ no na wɔde foro baeɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Ɔhene Salomo ne Israel asafo a wɔbɛhyiaa ne nkyɛn adaka no anim no nyinaa kunkumm nnwan ne anantwie a wɔn dodoɔ nti wɔantumi ankan na wɔammu ano, bobɔɔ afɔdeɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na asɔfoɔ no de AWURADE apam adaka no baa mu, de bɛsii n’afa, ɛdan no mpiakyire a ɛne kronkronkronbea no mu, kerubim no ntaban ase.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na kerubim no atrɛtrɛ wɔn ntaban mu, adaka no afa no so, na kerubim no kata adaka no ne ɛho mpoma no so ɔsoro.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na mpoma no woware ma wɔhunu mpoma no ti, adaka no ho, mpiakyire no anim, na wɔnhunu wɔ adihɔ hɔ, na ɛwɔ hɔ de bɛsi nnɛ da yi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Biribiara nni adaka no mu gye aboɔpono mmienu a Mose de guu mu Horeb, faako a AWURADE ne Israelfoɔ pameeɛ berɛ a wɔfiri Misraim asase so reba no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ, asɔfoɔ no firi kronkronbea hɔ firii adie no, (na asɔfoɔ a wɔhunuu wɔn no nyinaa ayɛ wɔn ho kronkron, na wɔanni nkyekyɛmu no akyi,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na Lewifoɔ nnwontofoɔ no a wɔhyɛ Asaf Heman, Yedutun ne wɔn mma ne wɔn nuanom aseɛ no nyinaa hyehyɛ nwera fɛfɛ, kurakura nnawuro ne mmɛnta ne nsankutene gyinagyina afɔrebukyia no apueeɛ fam, na asɔfoɔ ɔha aduonu ka wɔn ho rehyɛne ntotorobɛnto.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ntotorobɛntohyɛnfoɔ ne nnwontofoɔ no yɛɛ sɛ ɔbaakofoɔ maa wɔtee ɛnne baako a wɔde reyi AWURADE ayɛ da no ase), na wɔde ntotorobɛnto ne nnawuro ne nsankuo maa nne so yii AWURADE ayɛ sɛ, “ɔyɛ na n’adɔeɛ wɔ hɔ daa” no, ɛnna mununkum yɛɛ ɛdan no, AWURADE dan no ma,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na mununkum no nti asɔfoɔ no antumi annyina ansom, ɛfiri sɛ na AWURADE animuonyam ayɛ ɛdan no ma."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛnna Salomo kaa sɛ: AWURADE aka sɛ ɔbɛtena sum kusuu mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na me deɛ, masi tenabea mama wo, na masiesie baabi a wobɛtena hɔ daa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔhene danee n’ani hyiraa Israel badwa no nyinaa. Na Israel badwa no nyinaa gyina hɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔkaa sɛ: Nhyira ne AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn a ɔde n’ano kasa kyerɛɛ m’agya Dawid, na ɔde ne nsa ama no aba mu no sɛ:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛfiri da a mekɔyii me man Israel firii Misraim asase so baeɛ yi, menyii Israel mmusuakuo nyinaa mu kuro biara, sɛ wɔnsi dan na me din ntena hɔ, nanso menyii ɔbarima biara, sɛ ɔnni me man Israel so panin,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na mayi Yerusalem sɛ me din ntena hɔ, na mayi Dawid sɛ ɔnni me man Israel so.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɛwɔ m’agya Dawid akoma mu sɛ anka ɔbɛsi dan ama AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn din.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ m’agya Dawid sɛ: Ɛsiane sɛ na ɛwɔ w’akomam sɛ anka wobɛsi dan ama me din nti, woyɛɛ no yie sɛ na ɛwɔ w’akoma mu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nso ɛnyɛ wo na wobɛsi dan no, na wo ba a ɔfiri w’asene mu no, ɔno na ɔbɛsi dan ama me din.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na AWURADE ama n’asɛm a ɔkaeɛ no aba mu, na masɔre masi m’agya Dawid ananmu, na mete Israel ahennwa so, sɛdeɛ AWURADE kaeɛ no, na masi dan no mama AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn din,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na mede adaka a AWURADE apam a ɔne Israel mma pameeɛ no wɔ mu no masi hɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Salomo kɔgyinaa AWURADE afɔrebukyia no anim, Israel badwa no nyinaa anim, na ɔtrɛɛ ne nsam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Salomo ayɛ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ simpie bi de asi abannwa no mfimfini. Ne ntwemu basafa mmienu ne fa na ne terɛ basafa mmienu ne fa, na ne korɔn basafa baako ne fa, na ɔkɔgyinaa so. Na ɔkotoo ne nankoroma anim, Israel badwa no nyinaa anim, na ɔtrɛɛ ne nsam kɔɔ ɔsoro,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na ɔkaa sɛ: AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn, Onyankopɔn biara nni hɔ sɛ wo, ɔsoro ne asase so a wokora apam ne adɔeɛ ma wo nkoa a wɔde wɔn akoma nyinaa nante w’anim no,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> wo na woakora deɛ woka kyerɛɛ w’akoa, m’agya Dawid, no ama no. Wode w’ano na ɛkaeɛ, na wode wo nsa ama no aba mu, sɛdeɛ ɛteɛ nnɛ yi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na afei, AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn, kora deɛ woka kyerɛɛ w’akoa, m’agya Dawid, no so ma no, sɛdeɛ wokaa sɛ: Wɔremma onipa mmɔ no w’anim a ɔbɛtena Israel ahennwa soɔ. Hwɛ nko ara na wo mma nhwɛ wɔn akwan sɛ wɔbɛnante me mmara mu, sɛdeɛ wonantee m’anim no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na afei, AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn ma w’asɛm a woka kyerɛɛ w’akoa Dawid no ntim.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ampa sɛ Onyankopɔn bɛtena nnipa nkyɛn asase so anaa? Hwɛ, ɔsoro ne ɔsoro mu soro ntumi nkora wo, na nkantom ɛdan yi a masie yi!",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Nanso dane w’ani kyerɛ w’akoa mpaebɔ ne ne nkotosrɛ, AWURADE me Nyankopɔn, na tie nteamu ne mpaeɛ a w’akoa reyi no w’anim yi,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> sɛ w’ani bɛbue akyerɛ ɛdan yi awia ne anadwo, deɛ woka sɛ wɔmfa wo din nsi hɔ no, na woatie mpaeɛ a w’akoa rebɔ wɔ ha yi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na tie w’akoa ne wo man Israel nkotosrɛ a wɔde rebɔ mpaeɛ wɔ ha yi, na wo deɛ, firi wo tenabea ɔsoro hɔ, tie, na wote a, fa kyɛ!",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sɛ obi yɛ ne yɔnko bɔne na wɔde ntam gye no sɛ ɔnka, na ntam no ba w’afɔrebukyia anim efie yi mu a,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ɛnneɛ wo ara tie no ɔsoro, na yɛ, na bu wo nkoa atɛn, sɛ wobɛtua ɔbɔnefoɔ ka ama ne bɔne abua n’atifi, na woabu ɔteneneeni bem ama no sɛdeɛ ne tenenee teɛ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Sɛ wɔka wo man Israel gu wɔ atamfoɔ anim, sɛ wɔayɛ wo bɔne nti, na wɔsane bɛbɔ wo din, na wɔbɔ mpaeɛ na wɔkoto srɛ w’anim efie yi mu a,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ɛnneɛ wo ara tie no ɔsoro, na fa wo man Israel bɔne no kyɛ, na sane wɔn bra asase a wode maa wɔn ne wɔn agyanom no so.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Sɛ wɔto ɔsoro mu, na osuo ntɔ, sɛ wɔayɛ wo bɔne nti, na sɛ wɔbɛbɔ mpaeɛ kyerɛ ha yi, na wɔbɔ wo din, na wɔsane firi wɔn bɔne no ho sɛ woabrɛ wɔn aseɛ nti a,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ɛnneɛ wo ara tie no ɔsoro, na fa wo nkoa ne wo man Israel bɔne no kyɛ, na kyerɛ wɔn kwan pa a wɔmfa soɔ, na ma osuo ntɔ ngu w’asase a wode maa wo man sɛ agyapadeɛ no so.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Sɛ ɛkɔm ba asase yi so, sɛ ɔyaredɔm ba, sɛ ɔhoɔ ne ɔpoɔ, ntutummɛ ne mmɛbɛ ba, sɛ wɔn atamfoɔ bɛhiahia wɔn ho wɔn nkuro apono asase so a, ɔhaw biara oo, yadeɛ biara oo,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ɛnneɛ mpaebɔ biara, nkotosrɛ biara a onipa biara wɔ anaa wo man Israel nyinaa wɔ, na obiara nim ne haw ne ne yea, na ɔbɛtrɛ ne nsam akyerɛ efie yi no,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> wo ara tie no ɔsoro, wo tenabea hɔ, na fa kyɛ, na ma onipa no sɛdeɛ n’akwan nyinaa teɛ, sɛdeɛ wohunu n’akoma no. Na wo ara, wo nko ara na wonim nnipa mma akoma mu,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na wɔasuro woɔ, na wɔanante w’akwan soɔ nna a wɔde bɛtena asase a wode maa yɛn agyanom no soɔ no nyinaa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Afei nso ɔhɔhoɔ a ɔmfiri wo man Israel mu, na ɔfiri akyirikyiri asase bi so aba, wo din kɛseɛ ne wo nsa denden ne wo basa a woatene no nti no, sɛ ɔba bɛbɔ mpaeɛ ɛdan yi mu a,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> ɛnneɛ wo ara tie no ɔsoro, wo tenabea hɔ, na yɛ no sɛdeɛ ɔhɔhoɔ no su frɛ woɔ no nyinaa, deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na asase so amanaman nyinaa ahunu wo din, na wɔasuro wo sɛ wo man Israel, na wɔahunu sɛ wo din na wɔde frɛ efie a masie yi.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Sɛ wo man firi adi ne wɔn atamfoɔ kɔdi ako ɔkwan a wobɛsoma wɔn so, na wɔbɔ wo mpaeɛ kyerɛ kuro a woayie ne ɛdan a masi ama wo din yi a,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ɛnneɛ tie wɔn mpaebɔ ne wɔn nkotosrɛ no ɔsoro, na di wɔn asɛm ma wɔn.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Sɛ wɔyɛ wo bɔne, (ɛfiri sɛ onipa bi nni hɔ a ɔnyɛ bɔne,) na wofa wɔn ho abufuo na woyi wɔn ma wɔn atamfoɔ, na ɛdɔm soa wɔn kɔ asase bi so a, akyirikyiri oo, mmɛnkyɛneeɛ oo,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> na wɔma no ka wɔn akoma, asase a wɔafa wɔn akɔ hɔ no so, na wɔdane wɔn ho koto srɛ wo wɔn nnommumfafoɔ asase no so sɛ: Yɛayɛ bɔne, yɛafom na yɛadi abɔnefosɛm,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> na wɔde wɔn akoma nyinaa ne wɔn kra nyinaa sane ba wo nkyɛn, wɔn nnommumfafoɔ asase a wɔafa wɔn akɔ hɔ no so, na wɔbɔ mpaeɛ kyerɛ wɔn asase a wode maa wɔn agyanom ne kuro a woayie ne efie a masi ama wo din yi a,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> ɛnneɛ tie wɔn mpaebɔ ne wɔn nkotosrɛ ɔsoro, wo tenabea hɔ, na di wɔn asɛm ma wɔn, na fa wo man bɔne a wɔayɛ woɔ no kyɛ wɔn.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Afei, me Nyankopɔn, ma w’aniwa mmue ɛ, na yɛ aso ma ɛha yi mpaebɔ.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na afei, AWURADE Nyankopɔn, sɔre hyɛne wo homebea no mu, wo ne wo tumi adaka no. W’asɔfoɔ no, AWURADE Nyankopɔn, ma wɔnhyɛ nkwagyeɛ, na w’adɔeɛ nnipa ani nnye wo papa mu.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> AWURADE Nyankopɔn, nyi w’ani mfiri deɛ woasra no no so. Kae adɔeɛ a wode yɛɛ w’akoa Dawid no."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Salomo wiee ne mpaebɔ no, ogya firi soro ba bɛhyee ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne okum afɔdeɛ no, na AWURADE animuonyam bɛyɛɛ asɔredan no ma.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na asɔfoɔ no antumi anhyɛne AWURADE dan no mu, ɛfiri sɛ na AWURADE animuonyam no ayɛ AWURADE dan no ma.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Israel mma no nyinaa hunuu sɛ ogya ne AWURADE animuonyam aba efie no soɔ no, wɔde wɔn anim butubutuu fam aboɔ nsɛeɛ no so sɔree, na wɔdaa AWURADE ase sɛ, “ɔyɛ na n’adɔeɛ wɔ hɔ daa”.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔhene ne ɔman no nyinaa bɔɔ okum afɔdeɛ AWURADE anim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Ɔhene Salomo de anantwie mpemaduonu mmienu ne nnwan mpemha aduonu bɔɔ okum afɔdeɛ, na ɔhene ne ɔman no nyinaa dwiraa Nyankopɔn fie no ho.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na asɔfoɔ no gyinagyina hɔ, wɔn som nnwuma so, na Lewifoɔ no nso kurakura AWURADE nsankuo a Ɔhene Dawid yɛeɛ sɛ wɔmfa nna AWURADE ase, sɛ n’adɔeɛ wɔ hɔ daa, berɛ a Dawid nam wɔn so yii AWURADE ayɛ no. Na asɔfoɔ no hyenhyɛnee ntotorobɛnto, wɔn ntentensoɔ, na Israel nyinaa gyinagyina hɔ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Salomo yɛɛ abannwa a ɛwɔ AWURADE dan no anim no kronkron, na ɛhɔ na ɔbɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ na ɔhyee asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ ho sradeɛ no, ɛfiri sɛ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ afɔrebukyia a Salomo yɛeɛ no, na ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne aduane afɔdeɛ ne sradeɛ nam no nsene so.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛberɛ no mu no, Salomo dii nnapɔnna no nnanson, na Israel nyinaa ka ne ho, asafo kɛseɛ pa ara a wɔfiri deɛ wɔrekɔ Hamat kɔsi Misraim subonhwa ano.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɛda a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no, wɔyɛɛ afahyɛ nhyiamu, na afɔrebukyia no dwira, wɔdii no nnanson, ne nnapɔnna no nso, nnanson.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na bosome a ɛtɔ so nson no da a ɛtɔ so aduonu mmiɛnsa no, ɔgyaa ɔman no kwan maa wɔkɔɔ wɔn afie. Na wɔn ani gyee na wɔn bo tɔɔ wɔn yam, adepa a AWURADE ayɛ Dawid ne Salomo ne ne man Israel no nti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Salomo wiee AWURADE fie ne ɔhene fie no. Na deɛ ɛbaa Salomo akoma mu sɛ ɔbɛyɛ AWURADE fie ne ne fie mu no nyinaa wiee yie.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na AWURADE bɛyii ne ho kyerɛɛ Salomo anadwo, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Mate wo mpaebɔ, na mayi ha afa sɛ afɔrebɔ fie.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hwɛ, sɛ meto ɔsoro mu na osuo ntɔ, na sɛ mehyɛ ntutummɛ sɛ wɔmmɛdi asase no, na sɛ mede ɔyaredɔm ba me man mu,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na sɛ me man a wɔabɔ me din wɔ wɔn soɔ no brɛ wɔn ho ase na wɔbɔ mpaeɛ, na wɔhwehwɛ m’anim, na wɔsane firi wɔn akwammɔne no so a, me nso mɛfiri ɔsoro matie, na mede wɔn bɔne akyɛ, na masa wɔn asase no yadeɛ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Afei m’ani bɛbue na mayɛ aso mama ɛha yi mpaebɔ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na afei mafa efie yi ayɛ no kronkronbea, sɛ me din ntena hɔ nkɔsi daa, na m’ani ne m’akoma bɛtena hɔ nna nyinaa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wo deɛ, sɛ wonante m’anim sɛdeɛ w’agya Dawid nanteeɛ, sɛ wobɛyɛ deɛ mahyɛ woɔ nyinaa na woadi m’ahyɛdeɛ ne m’atemmudeɛ so a,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ɛnneɛ mɛma w’ahennie adwa atim, sɛdeɛ me ne w’agya Dawid pam sɛ meremma onipa a ɔbɛdi Israel soɔ mmɔ no no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na sɛ wo ne wo nkurɔfoɔ sane na mogya m’ahyɛdeɛ ne me mmara nsɛm a mede magu mo anim yi, na mokɔ kɔsom anyame foforɔ, na mosɔre wɔn a,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ɛnneɛ mɛtu mo afiri m’asase a mede memaa mo no so, na efie a mayɛ no kronkron ama me din yi, mɛto afiri m’anim atwene, na mede ayɛ ɛbɛ ne ɛfene aman nyinaa mu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɛdan a ɛkorɔn kɔ soro yi, obiara a ɔtwam ho no ho bɛdwiri no na waka sɛ: Ɛnam deɛn so nti na AWURADE ayɛ asase yi ne efie yi saa?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na wɔbɛka sɛ: Ɛfiri sɛ wɔagya AWURADE, wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn a ɔyii wɔn firii Misraim asase soɔ no, na wɔakɔsosɔ anyame foforɔ mu asɔre wɔn asom wɔn, enti na ɔde mmusuo yi nyinaa aba wɔn soɔ yi."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Salomo de mfeɛ aduonu sisii AWURADE fie ne ne fie no wieeɛ no,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ɔkyekyeree nkuro a Huram de maa no no, na ɔmaa Israelfoɔ kɔtenaa hɔ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Salomo sii mu kɔɔ Hamat-soba kɔdii so.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔkyekyeree Tadmor wɔ ɛserɛ so ne adekora nkuro a ɔkyekyeree no Hamat no nyinaa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔkyekyeree atifi Bet-horon ne anafoɔ Bet-horon, nkuro a ɛyɛ den a ɛwɔ afasuo ne apono ne apono akyi adaban;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ne Baalat ne adekora nkuro a Salomo wɔ no nyinaa ne nteaseɛnam nkuro nyinaa ne apɔnkɔsotefoɔ nkuro ne deɛ Salomo pɛɛ sɛ ɔkyekyeree no Yerusalem ne Lebanon ne n’ahennie asase no nyinaa so.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nso nkurɔfoɔ a wɔkaeɛ no a wɔfiri Hetifoɔ ne Amorifoɔ ne Perisifoɔ ne Hewifoɔ ne Yebusifoɔ mu a wɔmfiri Israelfoɔ no mu no nyinaa,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> wɔn mma a wɔkaa wɔn akyi wɔ asase no soɔ, a Israelfoɔ annwerɛ wɔn no mu bi, na Salomo gyee wɔn ɔhyɛ adwumayɛ toɔ de bɛsi nnɛ da yi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no mu deɛ, Salomo amfa obiara anyɛ akoa n’adwuma mu. Na wɔne n’akofoɔ ne n’akunini so asafohene, ne ne nteaseɛnam ne n’apɔnkɔsotefoɔ so asafohene.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na yeinom ne adwumayɛfoɔ a Ɔhene Salomo wɔ no so asafohene, nnipa ahanu aduonum a wɔdii nkurɔfoɔ no soɔ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Farao babaa no deɛ, Salomo de no firii Dawid kuro no mu baa efie a wasi ama no no mu, ɛfiri sɛ ɔkaa sɛ: Me yere nntena Israelhene Dawid fie, ɛfiri sɛ deɛ AWURADE adaka no aba no yɛ kronkron.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛno mu na Salomo bɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ maa AWURADE wɔ AWURADE afɔrebukyia a ɔsii no ntwonoowa no anim no soɔ,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> sɛdeɛ ɛhia da biara no, na ɔbɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no, sɛdeɛ Mose hyɛeɛ no, home nna deɛ ne abosome foforɔ deɛ; ne afahyɛ ahodoɔ mmiɛnsa a wɔhyɛ no afe biara, a ɛne: Apiti nnapɔnna, adapɛn nnapɔnna ne asese nnapɔnna.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na sɛdeɛ n’agya Dawid atorɔmudeɛ teɛ no, ɔde asɔfoɔ no nkyekyɛmu no sisii wɔn som so, ne Lewifoɔ no nso, wɔn som nnwuma so, sɛ wɔnyi ayɛ na wɔnsom asɔfoɔ no anim, sɛdeɛ ɛhia da biara; ne apono ano hwɛfoɔ no, wɔn nkyekyɛmu mu, ɛpono ne ɛpono ano, na saa na Nyankopɔn nipa Dawid hyɛeɛ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔamfiri ɔhene mmara asɛm a ɛda asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ no soɔ no ho, nsɛm nyinaa ne akoradeɛ no fam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Sei na wɔwiee Salomo adwuma no nyinaa; ɛfiri da a wɔtoo AWURADE fie fapem de kɔsi sɛ wɔwieeɛ. Sɛ wɔyɛɛ AWURADE fie no nie.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛno na Salomo kɔɔ Esion-geber ne Elot mpoano wɔ Edom asase so.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Huram nam ne nkoa so de ahyɛn ne nkoa a wɔnim po ho asɛm brɛɛ no, na wɔne Salomo nkoa kɔɔ Ofir, na wɔkɔfaa sika dwetikɛseɛ ahanan aduonum firi hɔ de brɛɛ Ɔhene Salomo."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Seba hemmaa tee Salomo nka no, ɔbaa sɛ ɔde nsɛm a emu yɛ den rebɛsɔ no ahwɛ. Na ɔne asafo yuu pa ne yoma a wɔsoso nnuhwam ne sika pii pa, ne abohene baa Yerusalem. Na ɔduruu Salomo nkyɛn no, ɔne no bɔɔ deɛ ɛwɔ n’akomam nyinaa ho nkɔmmɔ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Salomo buaa no ne nsɛm nyinaa, na asɛm biara anhunta Salomo a wanka ankyerɛ no.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Seba hemmaa no hunuu Salomo nyansa ne efie a wasie",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ne ne pono so nnuane, ne ne nkoa atenaeɛ, ne n’asomfo agyinaeɛ ne wɔn ntadeɛ, ne ne nsahyɛfoɔ ne wɔn ntadeɛ, ne n’aforoeɛ a ɔnam so kɔ AWURADE fie no, ne ho dwirii no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ ɔhene no sɛ: Wo nneyɛɛ ne wo nyansa ho asɛm a metee no m’asase soɔ no yɛ nokorɛ,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na mannye wɔn nsɛm no manni de bɛsii sɛ mebaeɛ, na mede m’ani mabɛhunu yi. Na hwɛ, wɔanka me wo nyansa so a ɛso no mu fa mpo, wosene wo ho nsɛm a meteeɛ no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nhyira ne wo nnipa, na nhyira ne wo nkoa yi a wɔgyinagyina w’anim daa yi, sɛ daa wɔte wo nyansa no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nhyira nka AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn a ɔpɛ w’asɛm na ɔde wo atena n’adwa so sɛ di hene ma AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn. Sɛ wo Nyankopɔn dɔ Israel, sɛ ɔde no bɛtim hɔ de akɔsi daa nti, na ɔde wo asi wɔn so hene, sɛ yɛ atemmudeɛ ne teneneedeɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔmaa ɔhene sika dwetikɛseɛ ɔha aduonu ne nnuhwam pii pa ara ne abohene, na nnuhwam a ɛte sɛ deɛ Seba hemmaa no de maa Ɔhene Salomo no so bi amma bio.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Huram nkoa ne Salomo nkoa a wɔde sika firi Ofir baeɛ no nso de abako nnua ne abohene bae.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔhene de abako nnua no yɛɛ AWURADE fie ne ɔhene fie ntrapoe ne nsankutene ne mmɛnta maa nnwontofoɔ no. Na wɔnhunuu saa nnoɔma no bi pɛn wɔ Yuda asase so.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Ɔhene Salomo maa Seba hemmaa no n’adeɛ a ɔpɛ a ɔbisaeɛ no nyinaa, ɛsono deɛ ɔde brɛɛ ɔhene no. Ɛnna ɔno ne ne nkoa sane sii mu kɔɔ n’asase soɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nso sika a na ɛba Salomo nsam afe baako mu duro yɛ sika dwetikɛseɛ ahansia aduosia nsia,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ɛsono deɛ ɛfiri adwadifoɔ hɔ, ne deɛ abatafoɔ de ba. Na Arabia ahemfo nyinaa ne asase no so amradofoɔ no nso de sika ne dwetɛ brɛɛ Salomo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Ɔhene Salomo de sika a wɔaborɔ yɛɛ akyɛm akɛseɛ ahanu, sika a wɔaborɔ nnwetɛbena ahansia na ɔde duraa akyɛm no mu biara ho.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ sika a wɔaborɔ akyɛm ahasa, sika nnwetɛbena ahasa na ɔde duraa akyɛm no mu biara ho. Na ɔhene de kɔsiee Lebanon Kwaeɛ dan no mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔhene de asonse yɛɛ ahennwa kokuroo, na ɔde sika amapa duraa ho;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na adwa no wɔ ntrapoe nsia, na sika ntiasoɔ wɔ adwa no ho a wɔabobɔ mu, na nsa wowɔ ɛha ne ha, atenaeɛ no ho, na agyata mmienu gyinagyina nsa no ho;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na agyata dummienu gyinagyina hɔ wɔ ntrapoe nsia no so ɛha ne ha. Wɔnyɛɛ saa bi da ahennie biara mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Ɔhene Salomo nnoɔma a ɔnom mu nyinaa yɛ sika, na Lebanon Kwaeɛ dan mu nnoɔma nyinaa yɛ sika amapa, dwetɛ nni mu. Wɔmmu dwetɛ hwee Salomo berɛ so.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔhene wɔ ahyɛnkuo a ɛne Huram nkoa no kɔ Tarsis; mfeɛ mmiɛnsa biara Tarsis ahyɛn no ba prɛko de sika ne dwetɛ, asonse ne nkontromfi ne nkokɔnini-abankwaa ba.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Ɔhene Salomo so senee asase so ahemfo nyinaa, adedodoɔ ne nyansa fam.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na asase so ahemfo nyinaa hwehwɛɛ sɛ wɔbɛhunu Salomo anim na wɔate nyansa a Onyankopɔn de ahyɛ n’adwene mu no bie.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na wɔde wɔn ayɛyɛdeɛ ba mmaako mmaako, dwetɛ nnoɔma ne sika nnoɔma ne ntadeɛ, akodeɛ ne nnuhwam, apɔnkɔ ne mfunumupɔnkɔ, afe biara ne ne deɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Salomo wɔ apɔnkɔ adan mpemnan ne nteaseɛnam ne apɔnkɔsotefoɔ mpem dummienu, na ɔde wɔn tenatenaa nteaseɛnam nkuro mu, ne ɔhene nkyɛn wɔ Yerusalem.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɔdii ahennie nyinaa so de firi Asuo Eufrate ano de kɔsii Filistifoɔ asase so ne Misraim hyeɛ so.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɔhene maa dwetɛ yɛɛ sɛ aboɔ, Yerusalem, na ntweneduro nso, ɔmaa no yɛɛ sɛ akyee nnua a ɛwɔ mpaperɛ soɔ no dodoɔ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wɔkraa apɔnkɔ firii Misraim ne nsase nyinaa so brɛɛ Salomo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Salomo ho nsɛm nkaeɛ, akane deɛ ne akyire yi deɛ no, wɔantwerɛ no Odiyifoɔ Natan nsɛm ne Siloni Ahia adiyisɛm ne Odehwɛfoɔ ldo adehwɛ a ɔhwɛɛ no Nebat ba Yeroboam ho no mu?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na Salomo dii Israel nyinaa so hene Yerusalem mfirinhyia aduanan.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na Salomo tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando, na wɔsiee no n’agya Dawid kuro mu. Na ne ba Rehoboam bɛdii n’adeɛ."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Rehoboam sii mu kɔɔ Sekem, deɛ na Israelfoɔ nyinaa aba sɛ wɔrebɛsi no hene.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Nebat ba Yeroboam a ɔwɔ Misraim, (deɛ ɔfiri Ɔhene Salomo anim dwane kɔeɛ no, tee). Ɛnna Yeroboam sane firii Misraim baeɛ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na wɔsoma maa wɔkɔhyiaa no bae, na Yeroboam ne Israel nyinaa ba bɛka kyerɛɛ Rehoboam sɛ:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> W’agya maa yɛn kɔnnua yɛɛ duru papa, na afei yi w’agya ɔsom denden, ne ne kɔnnua duruduro a ɔde too yɛn soɔ no ma no nyɛ hare, na yɛnsom wo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Ɛdi nnansa a, monsane mmra me nkyɛn bio. Na ɔman no kɔe.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Ɔhene Rehoboam ne mpanimfoɔ a n’agya Salomo da so te aseɛ no, na wɔsom no sɛ afotufoɔ no tuu agyina sɛ: Ɛfoɔ bɛn na moretu me na mede makɔbua ɔman yi?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Sɛ woyɛ ɔman yi yie, na wosɔ wɔn ani, na woka wɔn nsɛm pa a, ɛnneɛ wɔbɛyɛ wo nkoa nna nyinaa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔgyaa mpanimfoɔ no fo a wɔtuu no no, na ɔne mmɔfra a wɔne no nyiniiɛ a wɔsom no no kɔtuu agyina,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Ɛfoɔ bɛn na mo nso moretuo, na yɛde akɔbua ɔman yi a wɔbɛka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Yi kɔnnua a w’agya de too yɛn soɔ no so ma no nyɛ hare, no?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na mmɔfra a wɔne no nyiniiɛ no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Sei na ka kyerɛ ɔman yi a wɔbɛka kyerɛɛ wo sɛ: W’agya maa yɛn kɔnnua yɛɛ duru, na wo deɛ, yɛ no hare ma yɛn, no, sei na ka kyerɛ wɔn: Me kɔkorɔmmɔto so sene m’agya asene.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na sɛ, m’agya de kɔnnua duruduro soaa mo a, me deɛ, mɛto mo kɔnnua no so; m’agya de mpire na ɛhwee mo a, me deɛ, mede anyanyankyerɛ na ɛbɛhwe mo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Yeroboam ne ɔman no nyinaa baa Rehoboam nkyɛn da a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no, sɛdeɛ ɔhene kaa sɛ: Da a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no, monsane mmra me nkyɛn, no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔhene no de asɛm denden buaa wɔn, na Ɔhene Rehoboam gyaa mpanimfoɔ no fo a wɔtuu no no,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛdeɛ mmɔfra no tuu no foɔ no sɛ: M’agya maa mo kɔnnua yɛɛ duru, na me deɛ, mɛto so, m’agya de mpire na ɛhwee mo, na me deɛ, mede anyanyankyerɛ na ɛbɛhwe mo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔhene no antie ɔman no, ɛfiri sɛ Onyankopɔn na ɔdanee no saa, sɛdeɛ AWURADE bɛma n’asɛm a ɔnam Siloni Ahia so ka kyerɛɛ Nebat ba Yeroboam no aba mu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Israel nyinaa hunuu sɛ ɔhene no antie wɔn no, ɔman no buaa ɔhene no sɛ: Kyɛfa bɛn na yɛwɔ no Dawid mu? Na yɛnni agyapadeɛ biara nso Yisai ba no mu. O Israel, monkɔ mo afie! Afei, Dawid, hwɛ wo ara wo fie so. Ɛnna Israel nyinaa sii mu kɔɔ wɔn afie mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Israelfoɔ a na wɔtete Yuda nkuro mu no deɛ, Rehoboam dii wɔn so hene.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Ɔhene Rehoboam somaa Hadoram a ɔdi adwuma toɔ soɔ no, na Israelfoɔ no sii no aboɔ maa ɔwuiɛ. Ɛnna Ɔhene Rehoboam yɛɛ ntɛm foroo teaseɛnam sɛ ɔredwane akɔ Yerusalem.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Israel wae firii Dawid fie ho de bɛsi nnɛ."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Rehoboam duruu Yerusalem no, ɔboaa Yuda ne Benyamin fiefoɔ no nyinaa ano hyiae, nnipa a wɔayi wɔn akofoɔ mpemha aduɔwɔtwe, sɛ ɔne Israel rekɔko na wɔadane ahennie no ama Rehoboam.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa Nyankopɔn nipa Semaia nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ka kyerɛ Salomo ba Rehoboam, Yuda hene, ne Israelfoɔ a wɔwɔ Yuda ne Benyamin nyinaa sɛ:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sɛ AWURADE seɛ nie: Mommforo nnkɔ, na mo ne mo nuanom nnkɔko. Monsane nkɔ mo afie, na me na asɛm yi firi me. Na wɔtiee AWURADE asɛm no, na wɔne Yeroboam ankɔko.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Rehoboam tenaa Yerusalem. Na ɔkyekyeree nkuro maa no yɛɛ den wɔ Yuda,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na ɔkyekyeree Betlehem, Etam, Tekoa,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bet-sur, Soko, Adulam,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Gat, Maresa, Sif,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Adoraim, Lakis, Aseka,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Sora, Ayalon ne Hebron a ɛyɛ Yuda ne Benyamin mu nkuro a ɛyɛ den no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔhyehyɛɛ nkuro no den, na ɔde asafohene ne aduane ne ngo ne nsa akoradeɛ kokɔɔ mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔde akyɛm ne mpea hyehyɛɛ nkuro no nyinaa mu, na ɔhyehyɛɛ nkuro no den pa ara. Sɛ ɔdii Yuda ne Benyamin so ne no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ a na wɔwɔ Israel nyinaa mu firi wɔn ahyeɛ nyinaa so bɛgyinaa n’akyi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Lewifoɔ no gyigyaa wɔn nkuro ho mmoa adidibea nsase ne wɔn agyapadeɛ, na wɔbaa Yuda ne Yerusalem, ɛfiri sɛ Yeroboam ne ne mma tutuu wɔn sɛ wɔnnni AWURADE asɔfoɔ,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na ɔhyehyɛɛ n’asɔfoɔ maa sorɔnsorɔmmea no ne mpapo ne anantwie mma a ɔyɛeɛ no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wɔn akyiri no, wɔn a wɔde akoma maa sɛ wɔbɛhwehwɛ AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no fifirii Israel mmusuakuo nyinaa mu baa Yerusalem, sɛ wɔrebɛbɔ afɔdeɛ ama AWURADE wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wɔmaa Yuda ahennie no yɛɛ den, na wɔhyɛɛ Salomo ba Rehoboam den mfirinhyia mmiɛnsa, ɛfiri sɛ wɔnantee Dawid ne Salomo kwan so mfeɛ mmiɛnsa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Rehoboam waree Mahalat a ɔyɛ Dawid ba Yerimot babaa, ne Abihail a ɔyɛ Yisai ba Eliab babaa,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na ɔwoo mma, Yeus ne Semaria ne Saham maa no.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɛno akyiri no, ɔwaree Absalom ba Maaka, na ɔwoo Abia ne Atai ne Sisa ne Selomit maa no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Rehoboam dɔ Absalom ba Maaka sene ne yerenom ne ne mpenafoɔ nyinaa, (na ɔwaree yerenom dunwɔtwe ne mpenafoɔ aduosia, na ɔwowoo mmammarima aduonu nwɔtwe ne mmammaa aduosia).",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Rehoboam de Maaka ba Abia yɛɛ ne nuanom no mu tire ne panin, na ɔpɛɛ sɛ ɔsi no hene.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔdii no nyansam, na ɔde ne mmammarima no nyinaa mu binom sisii Yuda ne Benyamin nsase no nyinaa so nkuro a ɛyɛ den no nyinaa mu, na ɔde akɔnhomabɔdeɛ bebree maa wɔn, na ɔgyegyee mmaa bebree aware memaa wɔn."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Rehoboam ahennie timiiɛ, na ɔyɛɛ den no, ɔgyaa AWURADE mmara, na Israel nyinaa ka ne ho.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Ɔhene Rehoboam afe a ɛtɔ so nnum no Misraimhene Sisak foro baa Yerusalem so, ɛfiri sɛ na wɔafom AWURADE.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɔde nteaseɛnam apem ahanu ne apɔnkɔsotefoɔ mpemaduosia bae, na ɛdɔm a wɔne no baeɛ no nni ano, wɔfiri Misraim: Libiafoɔ, Sukifoɔ ne Etiopiafoɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔgyee Yuda nkuro a ɛyɛ den no, na ɔbɛduruu Yerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnna Odiyifoɔ Semaia baa Rehoboam ne Yuda mmapɔmma a wɔaboa wɔn ano aba Yerusalem afiri Sisak anim no nkyɛn, na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE seɛ nie: Mo deɛ, moagya me, na me nso magyaa mo ahyɛ Sisak nsa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna Israel mmapɔmma ne ɔhene no brɛɛ wɔn ho aseɛ, na wɔkaa sɛ: Ɔteneneeni ne AWURADE.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na AWURADE hunuu sɛ wɔabrɛ wɔn ho aseɛ no, AWURADE asɛm baa Semaia nkyɛn sɛ: Wɔabrɛ wɔn ho ase nti, merensɛe wɔn, na ɛyɛ kakra a mɛma wɔafiri mu afi, na m’abufuo amfa Sisak nsa so anhwie angu Yerusalem so.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nanso wɔbɛyɛ no nkoa, na wɔahunu me som ne nsase so ahennie som no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Misraimhene Sisak foro baa Yerusalem bɛfaa AWURADE fie akoradeɛ ne ɔhene fie akoradeɛ no, — ne nyinaa na ɔfaeɛ, — na ɔfaa sika akyɛm a Salomo yɛeɛ no nso.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Ɔhene Rehoboam yɛɛ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ akyɛm sisii ananmu, na ɔde hyehyɛɛ awɛmfoɔ a wɔwɛn ɔhene fie pono ano no asafohene no nsa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na da biara a ɔhene ba AWURADE fie no, awɛmfoɔ no bɛsoa kɔ na wɔde asane aba awɛmfoɔ no dan mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɛnam sɛ ɔbrɛɛ ne ho aseɛ nti, AWURADE abufuo no sane firii ne so, sɛ ɔrensɛe no nwie; na ɔmannwoeɛ wɔ Yuda mu nso.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Ɔhene Rehoboam hyɛɛ ne ho den wɔ Yerusalem, na ɔdii hene. Na ɔbɛdii hene no, na wadi mfeɛ aduanan baako, na ɔdii hene mfirinhyia dunson wɔ Yerusalem a ɛne kuro a AWURADE yii Israel mmusuakuo nyinaa mu sɛ ɔde ne din bɛto hɔ no. Na ne na din de Naama a ɔyɛ Amonni.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ bɔne, na wamfa n’akoma anhwehwɛ AWURADE.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Rehoboam ho nsɛm, kane deɛ ne akyire yi deɛ nso, wɔantwerɛ no Odiyifoɔ Semaia ne ɔdehunufoɔ Ido nsɛm mu antoatoa so? Na akodie daa Rehoboam ne Yeroboam ntam nna nyinaa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Rehoboam tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando, na wɔsiee no Dawid kuro no mu. Na ne ba Abia bɛdii n’adeɛ."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɔhene Yeroboam afe a ɛtɔ so dunwɔtwe soɔ no, Abia bɛdii Yuda so hene.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mfeɛ mmiɛnsa na ɔdii hene Yerusalem, na ne na din de Mikaia, Uriel ba a ɔfiri Gibea. Na ɛko baa Abia ne Yeroboam ntam.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Abia de mmarima akofoɔ dɔm a ano si nnipa a wɔayi wɔn mpemahanan kɔɔ ɔsa no, na Yeroboam de nnipa mpemahanwɔtwe, mmarima a wɔtumi wɔn ho a wɔayi wɔn ne no de bɛbɔɔ ani.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Abia sɔree Semaraim bepɔ a ɛwɔ Efraim mmepɔ soɔ no atifi, na ɔkaa sɛ: Yeroboam ne Israel nyinaa, montie me.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnyɛ mo deɛ, sɛ mobɛhunu sɛ AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no de Israel so ahennie ama Dawid, de rekɔsi daa sɛ nkyene apam ama ɔno ne ne mma anaa?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Nebat ba Yeroboam a ɔyɛ Dawid ba Salomo akoa no asɔre ate ne wuranom so atua,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na nnipa hunu ahuhufoɔ ne no boom hyɛɛ wɔn ho den tiaa Salomo ba Rehoboam, na Rehoboam yɛ abɔfra, na n’akoma yɛ mmerɛ, na wanhyɛ ne ho den wɔn anim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na afei, mo deɛ, mose mobɛhyɛ mo ho den, AWURADE ahennie a ɛwɔ Dawid mma nsam no anim, na moyɛ asafo yuu, na mowɔ sika anantwie a Yeroboam ayɛ ama mo sɛ anyame.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Montutuu AWURADE asɔfoɔ, Aaron mma no ne Lewifoɔ no na monyɛɛ asɔfoɔ mfaeɛ sɛ nsase so aman no? Obiara a ɔde nantwinini ba, anaa adwennini nson ba sɛ ɔrebɛdwira ne ho no bɛyɛ ɔsɔfoɔ ma deɛ ɛnyɛ anyame.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na yɛn deɛ, AWURADE ne yɛn Nyankopɔn, na yɛnnyaa no, na asɔfoɔ a wɔsom AWURADE no yɛ Aaron mma, na Lewifoɔ no kura wɔn adwuma mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔhye ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ma AWURADE daa anɔpa ne anwummerɛ ne ɔhyeɛ aduhwam no. Na wɔsiesie kyerɛ paanoo wɔ ɔpono kronkron no so, na sika kaneadua ne ne kanea no, wɔsɔ no daa anwummerɛ. Na yɛn deɛ, yɛyɛ AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn ahyɛdeɛ no, na mo deɛ, moagya no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na hwɛ, Onyankopɔn ka yɛn ho, di kan, ne n’asɔfoɔ a wɔhyɛne osebɔ ntotorobɛnto, sɛ wɔde bɛfrɛ ɔko atia mo. Israel mma, mo ne AWURADE mo agyanom Nyankopɔn no nnko, na ɛrensi mo yie.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Yeroboam maa atɛfoɔ buu wɔn ho braka na wɔabɛfiri wɔn akyi. Na wɔwɔ Yuda anim, na atɛfoɔ no wɔ wɔn akyire.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Yuda danedanee wɔn ani no, na hwɛ, ɛdɔm no wɔ anim ne akyire. Ɛnna wɔteaa mu frɛɛ AWURADE, na asɔfoɔ no hyenhyɛnee ntotorobɛnto.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Yuda mmarima no bɔɔ ose. Na ɛbaa sɛ Yuda mmarima no bɔɔ ose no, Onyankopɔn kaa Yeroboam ne Israel nyinaa gui, Abia ne Yuda anim.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no dii nkoguo wɔ Yuda anim, na Onyankopɔn de wɔn hyɛɛ wɔn nsa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Abia ne ne man kunkumm wɔn okumkɛseɛ, na asraafoɔ a wɔtotɔɔ Israel mu yɛ nnipa a wɔayi wɔn mpemahanum.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔbrɛɛ Israelfoɔ no ase berɛ no mu, na Yudafoɔ no ho yɛɛ den, ɛfiri sɛ na wɔtwere wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Abia tii Yeroboam, na ɔkɔgyee ne nsam nkuro, Betel ne ɛho nkurowa ne Yesana ne ɛho nkurowa ne Efron ne ɛho nkurowa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Yeroboam annya tumi biara bio Abia berɛ so. Na AWURADE kaa no maa no wui.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Abia hyɛɛ ne ho den, na ɔwarewaree yerenom dunan, na ɔwowoo mmammarima aduonu mmienu ne mmammaa dunsia.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Abia ho nsɛm nkaeɛ ne n’akwan ne ne nsɛm, wɔatwerɛ no Odiyifoɔ Ido nkyerɛaseɛ nwoma no mu."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Abia tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando, na wɔsiee no Dawid kuro mu, na ne ba Asa bɛdii n’adeɛ. Ne berɛ so na asase no so dwoo mfeɛ du.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Asa yɛɛ deɛ ɛyɛ na ɛtene AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn ani so,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ɔyiyii ananafoɔ afɔrebukyia ne sorɔnsorɔmmea no, na ɔdwirii adum no, na ɔtwitwaa Asera nnua no gui.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔhyɛɛ Yuda sɛ wɔnhwehwɛ AWURADE wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no, na wɔnni ne mmara ne n’ahyɛdeɛ no so.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔyiyii Yuda nkuro nyinaa so sorɔnsorɔmmea ne nnuhwam afɔremmukyia no. Na ahennie no mu dwoe wɔ n’ase.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔkyekyeree nkuro a ɛyɛ den Yuda, ɛfiri sɛ asase no so dwoe, na wanko ɔko biara mfeɛ no mu, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE maa no ɔhome.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ Yuda sɛ: Momma yɛnkyekyere nkuro yi, na yɛmfa ɔfasuo ne aban atentene, apono ne adaban ntwa ho nhyia. Asase yi da so da yɛn anim, ɛfiri sɛ yɛahwehwɛ AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn. Yɛahwehwɛ no, na wama yɛn ɔhome afa nyinaa ahyia. Na wɔkyekyeree, na ɛsii wɔn yie.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Asa wɔ dɔm a wɔkura akyɛm ne mpea mu, Yuda mu nnipa mpemahasa ne Benyamin mu nnipa a wɔkura akyɛm mu na wɔkuntunu tadua, mpemahanu aduɔwɔtwe, mmarima a wɔtumi wɔn ho ara nko.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Etiopiani Sera de dɔm a ano si apem ahodoɔ apem ne nteaseɛnam ahasa tu baa wɔn so, na ɔbɛduruu Maresa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Asa firii adi kɔhyiaa no, na wɔbaee wɔn mpasua mu wɔ Sefata bonhwa mu, Maresa ho.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Asa frɛɛ AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn sɛ: AWURADE, ɛnyɛ adeɛ bi mma wo sɛ wobɛboa wɔn a wɔdɔɔso anaa wɔn a wɔnni tumi. Boa yɛn, AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn, na wo na yɛtwere woɔ, na wo din mu na yɛnam rekɔ nnipakuo yi soɔ. AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn ne wo, mma ɔdasani nnnya wo so ahoɔden.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE kaa Etiopiafoɔ no guiɛ Asa ne Yuda anim, na Etiopiafoɔ no dwanee.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Asa ne nnipa a wɔka ne ho no tii wɔn kɔduruu Gerar. Na Etiopiafoɔ mu nnipa totɔe ara kɔsii sɛ wɔsaeɛ, na wɔdwerɛɛ wɔn pasaa, AWURADE ne ne dɔm anim. Na wɔfaa asadeɛ bebree pa ara.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔsɛee nkuro a ɛtwa Gerar ho hyia no nyinaa, na AWURADE ho hu kutaa wɔn. Na wɔfom nkuro no nyinaa, na na asadeɛ pii wɔ mu.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔsɛee mmoakuo ntomadan nso, na wɔfaa nnwan pii ne yoma kɔe, na wɔsane baa Yerusalem."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Nyankopɔn honhom baa Oded ba Asaria so,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na ɔfiri adi kɔhyiaa Asa, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Asa ne Yudafoɔ ne Benyaminfoɔ nyinaa, montie me. AWURADE ne mo te, sɛdeɛ mo ne no teɛ yi. Na sɛ mohwehwɛ no a, ɔbɛma moahu no, na sɛ mogya no a, ɔbɛgya mo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Israel nna bebree wɔ hɔ a wɔnni nokorɛ Nyankopɔn na wɔnni ɔsɔfoɔ a ɔkyerɛkyerɛ, na wɔnni mmara.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔn ahohiahia mu no, wɔsane baa AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn nkyɛn bɛhwehwɛɛ no no, ɔmaa wɔhunuu no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɛberɛ no mu no na asomdwoeɛ nni hɔ mma deɛ ɔfiri adie ne deɛ ɔba mu, na sakasaka bebree baa nsase no sotefoɔ nyinaa so.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔbobɔɔ wɔn ho, ɔman ne ɔman ne kuro ne kuro, na Onyankopɔn maa wɔn ani tanee ahohiahia nyinaa mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na mo deɛ, monhyɛ mo ho den, na mommma mo abasa mu nngo, na wɔbɛtua mo adwuma so ka.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Asa tee nsɛm yi ne Odiyifoɔ Oded adiyie no, ɔhyɛɛ ne ho den, na ɔyii atantanneɛ no firii Yuda ne Benyamin asase nyinaa so, ne nkuro a ɔgyee no Efraim bepɔ soɔ no mu, na ɔyɛɛ AWURADE afɔrebukyia a ɛwɔ AWURADE ntwonoowa no anim no foforɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔboaa Yuda ne Benyamin nyinaa ne ahɔhoɔ a wɔfiri Efraim ne Manase ne Simeon, ba bɛkaa wɔn ho no ano hyiae, na wɔhunuu sɛ AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn di n’akyire nti, nnipa pii wae firii Israel baa ne fam.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔboaa wɔn ano wɔ Yerusalem bosome a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no, Asa ahennie afe a ɛtɔ so dunum so.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔde asadeɛ a wɔde baeɛ no bi bɔɔ AWURADE afɔdeɛ da no, anantwie ahanson ne nnwan mpemnson,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na wɔne AWURADE yɛɛ apam sɛ wɔde wɔn akoma nyinaa ne wɔn kra nyinaa bɛhwehwɛ AWURADE wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na obiara a ɔrenhwehwɛ AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no, akumaa oo, ɔkɛseɛ oo, ɔbarima oo, ɔbaa oo, wɔnku no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔde nne kɛseɛ ne osebɔ ne ntotorobɛnto ne mmɛn suae kyerɛɛ AWURADE.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Yuda nyinaa ani gyee nsuaeɛ no ho, ɛfiri sɛ wɔn akoma nyinaa na wɔde suaeeɛ; na wɔn pɛ nyinaa so na wɔhwehwɛɛ no; na ɔmaa wɔhunuu no, na AWURADE maa wɔn ɔhome afa nyinaa hyiae.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Maaka a ɔyɛ Ɔhene Asa ne na nso, ɔtuu no firii ɔhemmaadie so, ɛfiri sɛ ɔyɛɛ ohoni maa Asera. Na Asa twaa ne honi no, bubuu no gɔsɔgɔsɔ, kɔhyee no Kidron subonhwa mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na sorɔnsorɔmmea no deɛ, wɔanyi amfiri Israel. Nanso Asa akoma dii mu ne nna nyinaa mu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔde n’agya akronkronneɛ ne ɔno ara n’akronkronneɛ baa Nyankopɔn fie: Dwetɛ, sika ne nnwinneɛ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na akodie biara amma de kɔsii Asa ahennie afe a ɛtɔ so aduasa nnum so."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Asa ahennie afe a ɛtɔ so aduasa nsia mu na Israelhene Baasa foro baa Yuda soɔ, na ɔkyekyeree Rama sɛ ɔde resi deɛ ɔfiri adie ne deɛ ɔba mu, Yudahene Asa fam kwan.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɛnna Asa yii dwetɛ ne sika firii AWURADE fie ne ɔhene fie akoradeɛ mu soma maa wɔde kɔmaa Siriahene Ben-hadad a ɔwɔ Damasko no sɛ:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Apam wɔ me ne wo ntam ne m’agya ne w’agya ntam; hwɛ, mabrɛ wo dwetɛ ne sika: Bra bɛbubu wo ne Israelhene Baasa apam no mu, na ɔmfiri me so nkɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Ben-hadad tiee Ɔhene Asa, na ɔsomaa ne dɔm so asafohene maa wɔkɔɔ Israel nkuro so, na wɔkɔbɔɔ Iyon ne Dan ne Abel-maim ne Naftali nkuro aduane akoraeɛ nyinaa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ Baasa teeɛ no, ɔgyaee Rama kyekyerɛ na ɔmaa n’adwuma no kae.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna Ɔhene Asa faa Yuda nyinaa, na wɔkɔsoaa Rama aboɔ ne nnua a Baasa de kyekyereeɛ no, na ɔde kyekyeree Geba ne Mispa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɛberɛ no mu no, Ɔdehunufoɔ Hanani baa Yudahene Asa nkyɛn bɛka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ɛnam sɛ wotweree Siriahene na woantwere AWURADE wo Nyankopɔn no nti, Siriahene dɔm no afiri wo nsa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Etiopiafoɔ ne Libiafoɔ no nyɛ dɔm a wɔdɔɔso bebree pa ara, dodoɔ ne nteaseɛnam ne apɔnkɔsotefoɔ mu? Na ɛnam sɛ wotweree AWURADE nti, ɔde wɔn hyɛɛ wo nsa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na AWURADE de n’ani kyini fa asase nyinaa so, sɛ ɔde ne denyɛ bɛdi ama wɔn a wɔn akoma di mu wɔ ne ho no. Yei mu woadi nkwaseasɛm, na ɛfiri seesei de rekorɔ yi, akodie bɛba wo so.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Asa nyaa ɔdehunufoɔ no ho abufuo, na ɔde no kɔtoo nneduadan mu, ɛfiri sɛ ɔfaa no yei ho abufuo. Nanso Asa hyɛɛ ɔman no mu binom so ɛberɛ no mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na hwɛ, Asa ho nsɛm, akane deɛ ne akyire yi deɛ no, hwɛ wɔatwerɛ no Yuda ne Israel Ahemfo Nwoma no mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Asa yaree ne nan, n’ahennie afe a ɛtɔ so aduasa nkron mu, na ne yadeɛ no ano yɛ den pa ara, nanso ne yadeɛ no mu no, wanhwehwɛ AWURADE, na mmom nnuruyɛfoɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Asa tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando, na ɔwuu n’ahennie afe a ɛtɔ so aduanan baako mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔsiee no n’asieeɛ a ɔbɔre faeɛ, Dawid kuro mu no mu. Na wɔde no too mpa a nnuhwam ahodoɔ a wɔafra no nnufrafoɔ kwan soɔ ayɛ so ma no so, na wɔhyee gya kɛseɛ pa maa no."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ne ba Yehosafat bɛdii n’adeɛ, na ɔhyɛɛ ne ho den ne Israel dii asie.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔde dɔm duaduaa Yuda nkuro a ɛyɛ den nyinaa mu, na ɔde bansifoɔ duaduaa Yuda asase so, ne Efraim nkuro a n’agya Asa gyeeɛ no mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na AWURADE dii Yehosafat akyi, ɛfiri sɛ ɔnantee n’agya Dawid kane akwan no so, na wanhwehwɛ Baalim,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na mmom n’agya Nyankopɔn na ɔhwehwɛɛ no, na ne mmara nsɛm so na ɔnanteeɛ, na ɛnyɛ sɛ Israel nneyɛɛ no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na AWURADE maa n’ahennie no timii wɔ ne nsam. Na Yuda nyinaa de ayɛyɛdeɛ brɛɛ Yehosafat, na ɔnyaa adedodoɔ ne animuonyam bebree.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔnyaa AWURADE akwan mu akoma pa; na afei ɔyiyii sorɔnsorɔmmea ne Asera nnua no firii Yuda.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na n’ahennie afe a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa mu no, ɔsomaa n’asafohene Ben-hail ne Obadia ne Sakaria ne Netanel ne Mikaia sɛ wɔnkɔ nkɔkyerɛkyerɛ Yuda nkuro mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Lewifoɔ Semaia, Netania, Sebadia, Asahel, Semiramot, Yonatan, Adoniya, Tobia ne Tob-Adoniya ka wɔn ho, na Asɔfoɔ Elisama ne Yehoram nso ka wɔn ho.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔkɔkyerɛkyerɛɛ Yuda; na wɔkura AWURADE mmara nwoma no, kyinii Yuda nkuro nyinaa mu, kyerɛkyerɛɛ ɔman no mu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na AWURADE ho hu baa nsase a ɛtwa Yuda ho hyia no ahennie nyinaa so, na wɔne Yehosafat anni ako.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔfiri Filistifoɔ mu nso de ayɛyɛdeɛ ne apeatoɔ dwetɛ brɛɛ Yehosafat, Arabiafoɔ mpo de nnwan brɛɛ no, adwennini mpemnson ahanson ne mpapo nso mpemnson ahanson.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Yehosafat kɔɔ so yɛɛ kɛse pa ara, na ɔtotoo aban ne aduanekora nkuro Yuda.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔwɔ adwuma bebree Yuda nkuro mu, na akofoɔ, mmarima a wɔtumi wɔn ho, Yerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔn dodoɔ sɛdeɛ wɔn mpanimfie teɛ nie: Yuda mu mpem mpem so asafohene ne: Ɔsafohene Adna, na mmarima a wɔtumi wɔn ho mpemahasa ka ne ho.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔno so na ɔsafohene Yehohanan die, na nnipa mpemahanu aduɔwɔtwe ka ne ho.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔno so na Sikri ba Amasia a ɔde ne ho maa AWURADE som kwa no die, na mmarima a wɔtumi wɔn ho mpemahanu ka ne ho.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Benyamin mu: Ɔbarima a ɔtumi ne ho Eliada, na nnipa mpemahanu a wɔkura ntadua ne akyɛm ka ne ho.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔno so na na Yehosabad die, na nnipa mpemha aduɔwɔtwe a wɔamia sɛdeɛ wɔrekɔ sa ka ne ho.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Yeinom ne wɔn a wɔsom ɔhene no, ɛsono wɔn a ɔhene de wɔn duaduaa Yuda nyinaa mu nkuro a ɛyɛ den no mu no."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Yehosafat nyaa ahodeɛ ne animuonyam bebree. Na ɔne Ahab bɔɔ nseɛ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na mfeɛ bi akyiri no, ɔsiane kɔɔ Ahab nkyɛn Samaria, na Ahab kunkumm nnwan ne anantwie bebree maa no ne nkurɔfoɔ a wɔka ne ho no. Na ɔgyegyee no sɛ ɔmforo nkɔ Ramot-gilead.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Israelhene Ahab bisaa Yudahene Yehosafat sɛ: Wo ne me bɛkɔ Ramot-gilead anaa? Na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Mete sɛ wo, na me man te sɛ wo man, me ne wo bɛkɔ ɔsa no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Yehosafat ka kyerɛɛ Israel hene no sɛ: Mesrɛ wo, kɔbisa AWURADE ansa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnna Israel hene no boaboaa adiyifoɔ no ano hyiaeɛ, nnipa ahanan, na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Yɛnkɔ Ramot-gilead nkɔko, anaasɛ mennyae? Na wɔse: Foro kɔ, na Onyankopɔn de bɛhyɛ ɔhene nsa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Yehosafat bisaa sɛ: AWURADE diyifoɔ biara nni ha bio, na yɛnkɔbisa ne hɔ adeɛ?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Israel hene ka kyerɛɛ Yehosafat sɛ: Ɔbarima baako da so wɔ hɔ a anka yɛbɛkɔ ne nkyɛn akɔbisa AWURADE hɔ adeɛ, nanso metane no, ɛfiri sɛ ɔnka me ho asɛm pa biara, na daa, bɔne na ɔka. Ɔno ne Imla ba Mikaia. Na Yehosafat se: Mma ɔhene nnka saa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛnna Israel hene no frɛɛ opiani bi, na ɔkaa sɛ: Ma Imla ba Mikaia mmra ntɛm.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Israel hene ne Yudahene Yehosafat tete wɔn adwa so, hyehyɛ wɔn ntadeɛ, na wɔtete Samaria pono ano mpraeɛ so. Na adiyifoɔ no nyinaa rehyehyɛ nkɔm, wɔn anim.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Kenaana ba Sedekia yɛɛ dadeɛ mmɛn, na ɔkaa sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE seɛ nie: Yeinom na wode bɛbobɔ Siriafoɔ no de akɔsi sɛ wɔbɛwie wɔn.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na adiyifoɔ no nyinaa hyehyɛɛ nkɔm saa sɛ: Foro kɔ Ramot-gilead na kɔdi nim; na AWURADE de bɛhyɛ ɔhene nsa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔbɔfoɔ a ɔkɔfrɛɛ Mikaia no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, adiyifoɔ no nsɛm yɛ koro, na ɛyɛ ma ɔhene, na ma w’asɛm nyɛ sɛ wɔn mu baako asɛm, na ka asɛmpa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Mikaia se: Sɛ AWURADE te aseɛ yi, deɛ me Nyankopɔn bɛka no, ɛno na mɛka.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔbaa ɔhene nkyɛn. Na ɔhene no bisaa no sɛ: Mikaia, yɛnkɔ Ramot-gilead nkɔko anaasɛ mennyae? Na ɔse: Monkɔ na monkɔdi nim, na wɔde bɛhyɛ mo nsa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔhene no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Mprɛ ahe ara na menka wo ntam sɛ, nka me asɛm biara sɛ nokorɛ nko AWURADE din mu?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛnna ɔse: Mehunuu Israel nyinaa sɛ wɔapansam mmepɔ soɔ sɛ nnwan a wɔnni hwɛfoɔ. Na AWURADE se: Yeinom nni wuranom? Ma wɔnsane nkɔ wɔn afie asomdwoeɛ mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnna Israel hene no ka kyerɛɛ Yehosafat sɛ: Manka mankyerɛ wo sɛ ɔrenhyɛ me ho nkɔm pa biara, na mmom bɔne?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Mikaia se: Enti montie AWURADE asɛm. Mehunuu AWURADE sɛ ɔte n’adwa soɔ, na ɔsoro asafo nyinaa gyinagyina ne nifa ne ne benkum.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na AWURADE se: Hwan na ɔbɛdaadaa Israelhene Ahab, na waforo akɔtua Ramot-gilead? Na oyi kaa sɛɛ, na oyi nso kaa sɛɛ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na honhom bi firi bɛgyinaa AWURADE anim, na ɔkaa sɛ: Me na mɛdaadaa no. Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Wode deɛn?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔse: Mɛfiri akɔyɛ honhom torofoɔ n’adiyifoɔ nyinaa anomu. Na ɔkaa sɛ: Wobɛdaadaa no, na wobɛtumi nso, firi kɔ na kɔyɛ saa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na afei, hwɛ, AWURADE de honhom torofoɔ ahyɛ w’adiyifoɔ yi nyinaa anomu, na AWURADE aka wo ho bɔne.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ɛnna Kenaana ba Sedekia twe piniiɛ bɛbɔɔ Mikaia sotorɔ kaa sɛ: Ɛhe na AWURADE honhom nam firii me nkyɛn bɛkasa kyerɛɛ woɔ yi?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Mikaia se: Hwɛ, ɛda a wobɛfiri pia mu akɔ pia mu akɔhunta na wobɛhunu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Israel hene no kaa sɛ: Momfa Mikaia nsane nkɔ kuro no safohene Amon ne ɔhene ba Yoas nkyɛn,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na monka sɛ: Sɛ ɔhene seɛ nie: Momfa oyi nkɔto nneduadan mu, na momma no ahohiahia aduane nni, ne ahohiahia nsuo nnom nkɔsi sɛ mɛba no dwoodwoo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na Mikaia se: Sane deɛ, wosane ba dwoodwoo a, ɛnneɛ na ɛnyɛ AWURADE na ɔnam me so kasaeɛ. Na ɔse: Mo aman nyinaa, montie!",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na Israelhene no ne Yudahene Yehosafat foro kɔɔ Ramot-gilead.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Israel hene no ka kyerɛɛ Yehosafat sɛ: Mɛsakyera me ho na makɔ dɔm no mu, na wo deɛ, hyɛ wo ntadeɛ. Na Israel hene no sakyeraa ne ho, na ɔkɔɔ dɔm no mu.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Nso na Siriahene no ahyɛ ne nteaseɛnam a ɔwɔ no so asafohene sɛ: Mone akumaa anaa ɔkɛseɛ nnko gye Israel hene no nko ara.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na nteaseɛnam so asafohene no hunuu Yehosafat no, wɔkaa sɛ: Israel hene no nie! Na wɔmane ne no kɔkoe. Na Yehosafat teaa mu; na AWURADE boaa no, na Onyankopɔn danee wɔn firii ne ho.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na nteaseɛnam so asafohene no hunuu sɛ ɛnyɛ Israel hene no ne no no, wɔsane firii n’akyi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na ɔbarima bi twee ne tadua mu, mpofirim so, na ɔto wuraa Israel hene no mmɔtoam ne nkataboɔ no ntam. Na ɔka kyerɛɛ ne teaseɛnamkafoɔ no sɛ: Dane w’ani na fa me firi ɛdɔm yi mu, na mapira.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na ɔko no mu yɛɛ den da no, na Israel hene no kura ne teaseɛnam mu gyina mu Siriafoɔ anim ara kɔsii anwummerɛ. Na owia kɔtɔeɛ no, ɔwui."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Yudahene Yehosafat sane baa ne fie asomdwoeɛ mu wɔ Yerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Hanani ba Yehu, ɔdehunufoɔ no, firi kɔhyiaa no, na ɔka kyerɛɛ Ɔhene Yehosafat sɛ: Ɔbɔnefoɔ na ɛsɛ sɛ woboa no, na wɔn a wɔtane AWURADE no na wodɔ wɔn? Na yei nti abufuo a ɛfiri AWURADE anim da wo so.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Nanso wɔahunu wo ho nsɛm pa, sɛ woatwitwa Asera nnua afiri asase no so, na woasiesie w’akoma ahwehwɛ Onyankopɔn.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Yehosafat tenaa Yerusalem. Na ɔsane firi kɔɔ ɔman no mu de firii Beer-seba kɔsii Efraim bepɔ so, na ɔdanee wɔ sane baa AWURADE wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no nkyɛn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔsisii atemmufoɔ asase no so, Yuda nkuro a ɛyɛ den nyinaa mu mmaako mmaako.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ atemmufoɔ no sɛ: Monhwɛ deɛ moreyɛ yie, na ɛnyɛ onipa na morebu atɛn ama no, na mmom AWURADE, na ɔne mo wɔ hɔ atemmuo asɛm no mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na afei AWURADE ho suro ntena mo so. Monhwɛ yie na monyɛ, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn no, nkontompo ne animhwɛ ne kɛtɛ-asehyɛ nni ne fam.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Yerusalem nso, Yehosafat de Lewifoɔ ne asɔfoɔ ne Israel agyanom atitire no mu binom sisii AWURADE atemmuo ne asennie so. Na wɔn atenaeɛ ne Yerusalem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔhyɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Sei na monyɛ wɔ AWURADE ho suro mu, nokorɛ ne mo akoma mu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Asɛm biara a ɛba mo anim a ɛfiri mo nuanom a wɔtete wɔn nkuro mu, na ɛyɛ mogya ne mogya ntam asɛm, anaa mmara ne ɛmom, ahyɛdeɛ ne atemmuo ntam asɛm no, monkyerɛkyerɛ wɔn mu, na wɔanni fɔ wɔ AWURADE anim, na abufuo amma mo ne mo nuanom so; monyɛ saa, na morenni fɔ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na hwɛ, Ɔsɔfoɔ Amaria na ɔda mo ano, AWURADE nsɛm nyinaa fam, na Ismael ba Sebadia a ɔyɛ Yuda fie bapɔmma no nso, ɔhene nsɛm nyinaa fam, na atemmufoɔ Lewifoɔ no nso wɔ mo anim. Mo ho nyɛ den na monyɛ, na AWURADE ne apapafoɔ bɛtena."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ ɛno akyiri no, Moabfoɔ, Amonfoɔ ne Maonfoɔ no mu binom a wɔka wɔn ho no baa Yehosafat so sɛ wɔne no rebɛko.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wɔbɛka kyerɛɛ Yehosafat sɛ: Ɛdɔm kɛseɛ bi firi po no agya firi Edom reba wo so, na hwɛ, wɔwɔ Hasason-tamar (a ɛne En-gedi no).",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Yehosafat suroe, na ɔyeree ne ho hwehwɛɛ AWURADE, na ɔpaee abuadadie Yuda nyinaa mu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Yudafoɔ boaboaa wɔn ano sɛ wɔrebɛhwehwɛ AWURADE hɔ mmoa. Yuda nkuro nyinaa mu na wɔfiri ba bɛhwehwɛɛ AWURADE.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Yehosafat sɔre gyinaa Yuda ne Yerusalem badwa no mu AWURADE fie abannwa foforɔ no anim,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na ɔkaa sɛ: AWURADE yɛn agyanom Nyankopɔn, ɛnyɛ wone Onyankopɔn wɔ soro, na wo ara na wodi amanaman ahennie nyinaa soɔ? Na wo nsam na tumi ne mmaninyɛ wɔ, na obiara nni hɔ a ɔbɛtumi agyina w’anim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛnyɛ wone yɛn Nyankopɔn a wotuu asase yi sofoɔ firii wo man Israel anim na wode maa wo dɔfo Abraham asefoɔ sɛ wɔntena so daa?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na wɔatena so, na wɔasi wo kronkronbea wɔ so maa wo din sɛ:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sɛ bɔne bi, sɛ afena, atemmuo anaa ɔyaredɔm, sɛ ɛkɔm ba yɛn so a, yɛbɛba abɛgyina efie yi anim ne w’anim, ɛfiri sɛ wo din wɔ efie yi mu, na yɛafiri yɛn amanehunu mu asu afrɛ wo, na woatie yɛn agye yɛn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na afei, hwɛ, Amonfoɔ, Moab ne Seir bepɔ a woamma Israel kwan amma wɔankɔ wɔn soɔ, berɛ a wɔfiri Misraim asase so reba no, na mmom wɔdane firii wɔn ho na wɔansɛe wɔn no,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> hwɛ, deɛ wɔde retua yɛn ka ne sɛ wɔaba rebɛtu yɛn afiri w’agyapadeɛ a wɔde maa yɛn sɛ yɛnni soɔ no soɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Yɛn Nyankopɔn, woremmu wɔn atɛn? Na yɛnni tumi a yɛde regyina ɛdɔm bebree yi a wɔreba yɛn soɔ yi anim. Na yɛn deɛ, yɛnnim deɛ yɛnyɛ, na wo so na yɛn ani da.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Yudafoɔ nyinaa gyinagyina AWURADE anim, wɔn ne wɔn mma nketewa, wɔn yerenom ne wɔn mma.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Matania ba Yeiel ba Benaia ba Sakaria ba Yehasiel a ɔyɛ Lewini a ɔfiri Asaf mma mu no, AWURADE honhom baa ne so badwa no mu,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na ɔkaa sɛ: Yuda nyinaa ne Yerusalemfoɔ ne Ɔhene Yehosafat, montie! Sɛ AWURADE se mo nie: Mo deɛ, monnsuro na mo akoma nntu dɔm bebree yi anim, na ɛnyɛ mo na ɔsa yi wɔ mo, na ɛwɔ Onyankopɔn.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɔkyena, monsiane nkɔ wɔn so, hwɛ, wɔreforo Sis aforoeɛ aba, na mobɛkɔ akɔto wɔn bonhwa no awieeɛ Yeruel serɛ anim.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnyɛ mo deɛ sɛ mobɛko yei mu, gyina nko ara na monkɔgyina, na monhwɛ AWURADE a ɔka mo ho no nkwagyeɛ. Yuda ne Yerusalem, monnsuro na mo akoma nntu, ɔkyena momfiri adi nkɔhyia wɔn, na AWURADE bɛdi mo akyi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛnna Yehosafat koto de n’anim butuu fam, na Yudafoɔ ne Yerusalemfoɔ no nyinaa hwehwee fam AWURADE anim sɔree AWURADE.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Lewifoɔ a wɔfiri Kohatfoɔ mma mu ne Korafoɔ mma mu no sɔree sɛ wɔde ɛnne kɛseɛ pa ara reyi AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no ayɛ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wɔsɔree anɔpatutu, na wɔfirii adi kɔɔ Tekoa serɛ so. Na wɔrefiri adie no, Yehosafat gyinae na ɔkaa sɛ: Yuda ne Yerusalemfoɔ, montie me. Monnye AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn nni, na mobɛtim, na monnye n’adiyifoɔ no nni, na mobɛdi yie.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔne ɔman no tuu agyina, na ɔyiyii nnwontofoɔ a wɔto AWURADE dwom yi no ayɛ, ahokeka kronkron mu; na wɔrefiri adie no, wɔdii wɔn a wɔamia no anim, na wɔkaa sɛ: Monna AWURADE ase, na n’adɔeɛ wɔ hɔ daa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɛberɛ a wɔrefiri dwontoɔ ne ayeyie aseɛ no, AWURADE maa atɛfoɔ baa Amonfoɔ, Moab ne Seir bepɔ sofoɔ a wɔbaa Yuda soɔ no so, na wɔkaa wɔn gui.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Amonfoɔ ne Moabfoɔ no sɔre tiaa Seir bepɔ sofoɔ no sɛee wɔn pasapasa. Na wɔwiee Seirfoɔ no, wɔboaa wɔn ho wɔn ho kunkumm wɔn ho wɔn ho.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Yuda duruu ahwɛeɛ a ɛhwɛ ɛserɛ soɔ, na wɔdanee wɔn ani hwɛɛ dɔm kɛseɛ no, na hwɛ, wɔn afunu na ɛgugu fam, na obi amfiri mu amfi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Yehosafat ne ne dɔm no kɔ kɔfomm wɔn asadeɛ no, na wɔhunuu wɔn mu ahodeɛ ne ntadeɛ ne nnwinneɛ a ɛyɛ fɛ pii pa ara, na wɔtase fae a na wɔntumi nsoa, na wɔde nnansa fomm asadeɛ no, ɛfiri sɛ na ɛdɔɔso bebree.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na da a ɛtɔ so nnan no, wɔboaboaa wɔn ano wɔ Beraka Bonhwa no mu, ɛfiri sɛ ɛhɔ na wɔhyiraa AWURADE, enti na wɔfrɛ ɛhɔ din sɛ “Beraka-Bonhwa” de bɛsi nnɛ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na Yuda ne Yerusalemfoɔ nyinaa sanee, na Yehosafat di wɔn anim, na wɔde anigyeɛ sane baa Yerusalem. Na AWURADE maa wɔn ani gyee wɔn atamfoɔ ho.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wɔkurakura mmɛnta ne asankuten ne ntotorobɛnto baa Yerusalem bɛhyɛnee no AWURADE fie.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na wɔtee sɛ AWURADE ne Israel atamfoɔ ako no, Nyankopɔn ho hu kaa nsase so ahennie nyinaa.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na Yehosafat ahemman mu dwoe, na ne Nyankopɔn maa no ɔhome afa nyinaa hyiae.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na Yehosafat dii Yuda so hene. Ɔbɛdii hene no, na wadi mfeɛ aduasa nnum, na ɔdii hene mfirinhyia aduonu nnum wɔ Yerusalem. Na ne na din de Asuba a ɔyɛ Silhi ba.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na ɔnantee n’agya Asa kwan so, na wammane amfiri so, na ɔyɛɛ deɛ ɛtene AWURADE ani so.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Nanso sorɔnsorɔmmea no deɛ, wanyi, na ɔman no nnya nsiesiee wɔn akoma mmaa wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na Yehosafat ho nsɛm nkaeɛ, akane deɛ ne akyire yi deɛ no, hwɛ, wɔatwerɛ no Hanani ba Yehu nsɛm a wɔde hyɛɛ Israel ahemfo nwoma mu no mu.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na ɛno akyiri no, Yudahene Yehosafat ne Israelhene Ahasia a ɔdii nsɛmmɔne no pamee.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na ɔne no pam sɛ wɔbɛyeyɛ ahyɛn akɔ Tarsis, na wɔpempam ahyɛn no Esion-geber.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na Dodafahu ba Eliesa a ɔfiri Maresa hyɛɛ Yehosafat ho nkɔm sɛ: Sɛ wo ne Ahasia apam nti, AWURADE asɛe wo nnwuma. Na ahyɛn no bobɔe, na wɔantumi ankɔ Tarsis."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Yehosafat tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando, na wɔsiee no kaa n’agyanom ho wɔ Dawid kuro no mu, na ne ba Yehoram bɛdii n’adeɛ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔwɔ nuammarima a wɔyɛ Yehosafat mma, wɔn ne Asaria, Yehiel, Sakaria, Asaria, Mikael ne Sefatia. Yeinom nyinaa yɛ Yudahene Yehosafat mma.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na wɔn agya maa wɔn akyɛdeɛ bebree, dwetɛ ne sika ne aboɔdenneɛ ne Yuda mu nkuro a ɛyɛ den bi nso, na ahennie no deɛ, ɔde maa Yehoram, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔno ne abakan.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Yehoram dii n’agya adeɛ na n’ahennie gyinaa pintinn no, ɔde nkrantɛ kunkumm ne nuammarimanom nyinaa ne Israel mmapɔmma mu binom nso.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Yehoram dii mfeɛ aduasa mmienu na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ nwɔtwe wɔ Yerusalem.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔnantee Israel ahemfo kwan so, sɛdeɛ Ahab fie yɛeɛ no, ɛfiri sɛ Ahab babaa yɛ ne yere, na ɔyɛɛ AWURADE ani so bɔne.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nanso AWURADE ampɛ sɛ ɔsɛe Dawid fie no, apam a ɔne Dawid pameeɛ no nti, ne sɛ ɔkaa sɛ: Ɔbɛma no ne ne mma nso kanea nna nyinaa no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ne berɛ so na Edom tee atua firii Yuda nsa aseɛ, na wɔkɔsii wɔn so hene.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Yehoram ne n’asafohene ne nteaseɛnam a ɛka ne ho nyinaa sene kɔɔ hɔ. Na ɔsɔree anadwo na ɔkɔkum Edomfoɔ a wɔatwa ne ho ahyia ne nteaseɛnam so asafohene no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Edom tee atua firii Yuda ase de bɛsi nnɛ. Ɛno na Libna nso tee atua berɛ no ara mu firii n’aseɛ, ɛfiri sɛ wagya AWURADE, n’agyanom Nyankopɔn no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nso ɔyeyɛɛ sorɔnsorɔmmea Yuda mmepɔ so, na ɔde Yerusalemfoɔ kɔɔ adwamammɔ mu, na ɔhyɛɛ Yuda maa wɔkɔɔ bɔne mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na krataa bi firi Odiyifoɔ Elia hɔ baa ne nkyɛn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE w’agya Dawid Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ woannante w’agya Yehosafat akwan soɔ ne Yudahene Asa akwan soɔ,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na wonantee Israel ahemfo akwan soɔ, na wode Yuda ne Yerusalemfoɔ kɔɔ adwamammɔ mu sɛ Ahab fie adwamammɔ no, na woakum wo nuanom nso, w’agya fiefoɔ a wɔyɛ sene woɔ no nti,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> hwɛ, AWURADE de ɔhaw kɛseɛ bɛha wo man ne wo mma ne wo yerenom ne w’ahodeɛ nyinaa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wo ara nso, wobɛyare. Wobɛyare wo yam de bɛkɔ akɔsi sɛ yadeɛ no nti w’ayamdeɛ bɛfiri adi da biara.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na AWURADE hwanyann Filistifoɔ ne Arabfoɔ a wɔwɔ Etiopiafoɔ nkyɛn mu no honhom tiaa Yehoram.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wɔforo baa Yuda so, na wɔtetee mu, na wɔfaa ahodeɛ a wɔhunuu no ɔhene fie nyinaa ne ne mmammarima nso ne ne yerenom nnommum kɔe, na anka ɔbabarima amma no gye ne mmammarima mu akumaa Yehoahas.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na yei nyinaa akyiri no, AWURADE de yafunu yadeɛ mu yadeɛ a ɛnni sabea bɔɔ no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na yei kɔɔ so ara kɔsii sɛ, mfeɛ mmienu awieeɛ no, n’ayamdeɛ firii adie yadeɛ no ara mu, na ɔwuu yea kɛseɛ mu. Na ne man ansɔ ogya biara amma no sɛ n’agyanom deɛ no.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɔdii mfeɛ aduasa mmienu na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ nwɔtwe wɔ Yerusalem. Na ɔkɔe, na obi annyam no. Na wɔsiee no Dawid kuro mu, nanso ɛnyɛ ahemfo no adamena no mu."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Yerusalemfoɔ de ne ba kumaa Ahasia sii hene n’ananmu, ɛfiri sɛ ne mma mpanimfoɔ no nyinaa, afomfafoɔ asafo a wɔne Arabfoɔ no baa nsra mu no kunkumm wɔn. Na Yehoram ba Ahasia dii Yuda hene.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ahasia dii mfeɛ aduanan mmienu na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene afe baako wɔ Yerusalem. Na ne na din de Atalia a ɔyɛ Omri ba.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɔno nso nantee Ahab fie akwan so, ɛfiri sɛ ne na tuu no fo sɛ ɔnni asɛmmɔne.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ AWURADE ani so bɔne sɛ Ahab fie, ɛfiri sɛ n’agya wuo akyiri no wɔn na wɔtuu no foɔ, na ɛmaa no guu asu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Wɔn afotuo nso so na ɔnam kɔeɛ, na ɔne Israelhene Yehoram a ɔyɛ Ahab ba kɔɔ ɔsa ne Siriahene Hasael kɔkoe wɔ Ramot-gilead. Na Siriafoɔ no piraa Yehoram.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔsanee sɛ ɔrekɔsa ne ho yadeɛ Yesreel afiri pira a ɔne Siriahene Hasael reko no, wɔpirapiraa no Rama no mu. Na Yudahene Yehoram ba Asaria siane kɔɔ sɛ ɔrekɔhwɛ Ahab ba Yehoram Yesreel, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔyare.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Onyankopɔn na ɔde asiane bɛsianee Ahasia sɛ ɔnkɔ Yehoram nkyɛn. Na ɔduruiɛ no, ɔne Yehoram fie kɔhyiaa Nimsi ba Yehu a AWURADE asra no sɛ ɔnsɛe Ahab fie.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Yehu rebu Ahab fie atɛn no, ɔkɔtoo Yuda mmapɔmma ne Ahasia nuanom mma a wɔsom Ahasia no, na ɔkunkumm wɔn.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔkɔhwehwɛɛ Ahasia, na wɔkyeree no, na ɔno deɛ, na ɔde ne ho ahunta Samaria. Na wɔde no brɛɛ Yehu, na wɔkumm no. Na wɔsiee no, na wɔkaa sɛ: Yehosafat a ɔde n’akoma nyinaa hwehwɛɛ AWURADE no ba ne no. Na obiara nni Ahasia fie bio a ɔbɛnya ahennie no ho ahoɔden.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Ahasia na Atalia hunuu sɛ ne ba awuo no, ɔsɔre kɔdwerɛɛ adehyeɛ a wɔwɔ Yuda fie nyinaa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔhene babaa Yehosabat faa Ahasia ba Yoas, na ɔwiaa no firii ɔhene mma a wɔreku wɔn no mu, na ɔde no ne ne ɔbagyegyefoɔ hyɛɛ pia mu. Na sɛ Ɔhene Yehoram babaa Yehosabat a ɔyɛ Ɔsɔfoɔ Yehoiada yere no yɛ Ahasia nuabaa nti, ɔde no hunta firii Atalia anim, na wanku no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔne wɔn tenaa Nyankopɔn fie, huntaa mfeɛ nsia. Na Atalia dii asase no so hemmaa."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na afe a ɛtɔ so nson mu no, Yehoiada sii ne bo faa ɔha ha so asafohene Yeroham ba Asaria, ne Yohanan ba Ismael, ne Obed ba Asaria ne Adaia ba Maaseia ne Sikri ba Elisafat maa wɔne no pamee.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wɔkyinii Yuda, na wɔboaboaa Lewifoɔ no ano firi Yuda nkuro nyinaa mu, ne Israel agyanom atitire no, na wɔbɛhyiaa wɔ Yerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na badwa no nyinaa ne ɔhene pamm wɔ Nyankopɔn fie. Na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Hwɛ, ɔhene ba no na ɔbɛdi hene, sɛdeɛ AWURADE aka no Dawid mma ho no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Adeɛ a monyɛ nie: Mo mu asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ a wɔba asɔrefie homeda no mu nkyɛmu mmiɛnsa mu baako mmɛyɛ ɛpono ano ahwɛfoɔ;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na nkyɛmu baako ntena ɔhene fie, na nkyɛmu baako nso ntena nnyinasoɔ pono no ano, na ɔman no nyinaa ntena AWURADE fie abannwa no so.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na obiara nnhyɛne AWURADE fie gye asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ mu wɔn a wɔsom no, wɔn na wɔnhyɛne mu, ɛfiri sɛ wɔyɛ kronkron, na ɔman no nyinaa nhwɛ AWURADE ahyɛdeɛ no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Lewifoɔ no ntwa ɔhene ho nhyia, wɔn akodeɛ nkurakura wɔn nsam. Na deɛ ɔhyɛne efie hɔ no, wɔnku no. Na wɔntena ɔhene no ho n’adifire ne ne muba mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Lewifoɔ no ne Yuda nyinaa yɛɛ sɛdeɛ Ɔsɔfoɔ Yehoiada hyɛeɛ no nyinaa. Na wɔn mu biara de ne nnipa a wɔrebɛsom asɔrefie homeda, ne wɔn a wɔrepɔn adwuma homeda no bae, ɛfiri sɛ Ɔsɔfoɔ Yehoiada amma wɔn a wɔrepɔn no ampɔn.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Ɔsɔfoɔ Yehoiada de Ɔhene Dawid mpea ne akyɛm akɛseɛ ne nkumaa a ɛwowɔ Nyankopɔn fie no memaa ɔha ha so asafohene no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔde ɔman no nyinaa gyinagyinaa hɔ, na wɔn akodeɛ kurakura wɔn nsam, ɛfiri ɛdan no nifa ntweaso kɔsi ɛdan no benkum ntweaso, afɔrebukyia no ne ɛdan no ho twaa ɔhene no ho hyiae.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔyii ɔhene ba no firii adi, na wɔde ahemmotire no hyɛɛ ne ti, na wɔde adanseɛ no maa no, na wɔsii no hene, na Yehoiada ne ne mma sraa no ngo, na wɔkaa sɛ: Ɔhene tiri nkwa!",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnna Atalia tee ɔman a wɔretu mmirika na wɔreyi ɔhene ayɛ no gyegyeegye no, ɔbaa nkurɔfoɔ no nkyɛn AWURADE fie,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na ɔbɛhunui, na hwɛ, na ɔhene no gyina n’agyinaeɛ aboboano, asafohene ne ntotorobɛnto no wɔ ɔhene no nkyɛn, na asase no so nkurɔfoɔ nyinaa ani agye, na wɔrehyenhyɛne ntotorobɛnto, na nnwontofoɔ no de nsankuo bɔɔ ayeyie nnwom. Ɛnna Atalia sunsuanee n’atadeɛ mu, na ɔkaa sɛ: Atirisopam, atirisopam!",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Yehoiada yii ɔha ha so asafohene a wɔhwɛ dɔm no soɔ no, na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Monyi no mfiri nkɔ nkyerɛpɛn no mu, na deɛ ɔbɛdi n’akyire no, wɔnku no nkrantɛ ano. Na ɔsɔfoɔ no kaa sɛ: Monnku no wɔ AWURADE fie.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔsɔɔ ne mu de no kɔɔ apɔnkɔ pono ano, ahemfie, na wɔkumm no wɔ hɔ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛnna Yehoiada de apam too ɔno ne ɔman no nyinaa ne ɔhene no ntam sɛ wɔnyɛ AWURADE man.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔman no nyinaa kɔɔ Baal fie kɔdwirii gui, na n’afɔrebukyia ne n’ahoni no, wɔbubui, na Baal sɔfoɔ Matan nso, wɔkumm no afɔrebukyia no anim.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Yehoiada siesiee AWURADE fie hwɛ nnwuma no de hyɛɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔne Lewifoɔ a Dawid kyekyɛɛ wɔn mu sisii AWURADE fie so, sɛ wɔmmɔ AWURADE ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no Mose mmara mu no, na wɔnyɛ no anigyeɛ ne nnwontoɔ mu sɛ Dawid hyehyɛɛ no no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Nanso ɔde apono ano ahwɛfoɔ gyinagyinaa AWURADE fie apono no ano, na deɛ ne ho nte biara, anhyɛne mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɔfaa ɔha ha so asafohene no ne aberempɔn no ne ɔman no sodifoɔ ne asase no sofoɔ nyinaa, na ɔde ɔhene no firii AWURADE fie sianee, na wɔbaa ɔhene fie pono a ɛkorɔn no mu, na wɔde ɔhene no tenaa ahennie adwa no so.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na asase no sofoɔ nyinaa ani gyee, na kuro no mu dwoe. Na Atalia deɛ, wɔde nkrantɛ kumm no."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Yoas dii mfeɛ nson na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ aduanan wɔ Yerusalem, na ne na din de Sibia a ɔfiri Beer-seba.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Yoas yɛɛ deɛ ɛtene AWURADE ani so Ɔsɔfoɔ Yehoiada berɛ no so nyinaa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Yehoiada waree yerenom baanu maa no, na ɔwoo mmammarima ne mmammaa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɛno akyiri no ɛbaa Yoas akoma mu sɛ ɔbɛsiesie AWURADE fie no foforɔ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔboaboaa asɔfoɔ no ne Lewifoɔ no ano hyiae, na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Momfiri adi nkɔ Yuda nkuro so, na monkɔgyegye dwetɛ mfiri Israel nyinaa nsam, na wɔde apempam mo Nyankopɔn fie no daa afe; na mo deɛ, momma mo ho nyɛ hare asɛm yi mu. Nanso Lewifoɔ no ho anyɛ hare.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna ɔhene no frɛɛ Ɔpanin Yehoiada, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Adɛn nti na womma Lewifoɔ no nnye Yuda ne Yerusalem toɔ a AWURADE akoa Mose ne Israel badwa no hyɛ maa adanseɛ ntomadan no?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Atalia, ɔbɔnefoɔ no mma ahyɛne Nyankopɔn fie no mu, na AWURADE fie akronkronneɛ nyinaa nso, wɔahwere ama Baalim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔhene no ka maa wɔpamm adaka baako, na wɔde sii AWURADE fie pono ano wɔ adihɔ,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na wɔpaee no Yuda ne Yerusalem sɛ wɔmfa Nyankopɔn akoa Mose toɔ a ɔde too Israel so wɔ ɛserɛ so no mmrɛ AWURADE.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na mmapɔmma no nyinaa ne ɔman no nyinaa ani gyee. Na wɔde ba bɛguu adaka no mu ara kɔsii sɛ ɛyɛɛ ma.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na berɛ biara a Lewifoɔ no bɛhunu sɛ sika adɔɔso wɔ adaka no mu no, wɔde brɛ wɔn a ɔhene ahyɛ sɛ wɔnhwɛ soɔ no; ɔhene twerɛfoɔ ne deɛ ɔsɔfo panin no ahyɛ sɛ ɔnhwɛ soɔ no ba bɛhwie firi adaka no mu, na wɔma so sane de kɔsi ne sibea. Saa na na wɔyɛ no da biara, na wɔboaboaa sika bebree ano.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔhene ne Yehoiada de maa wɔn a wɔyɛ AWURADE fie som adwuma no, na wɔde bobɔɔ aboɔpaefoɔ ne adwumfoɔ paa sɛ wɔnsiesie AWURADE fie no foforɔ, ne dadeɛ ne kɔbere mfrafraeɛ adwumfoɔ nso, sɛ wɔmmiamia AWURADE fie no mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔn a wɔyɛ adwuma no yɛe, na pempam adwuma no kɔɔ so wɔn nsam, na wɔde Nyankopɔn fie no sii hɔ maa no yɛɛ yie na ɛyɛɛ den.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔwieeɛ no, wɔde sika no nkaeɛ baa ɔhene ne Yehoiada anim, na wɔde yɛɛ nnoɔma maa AWURADE fie, ɔsom ne ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no ho nnoɔma ne nkoraa ne sika ne dwetɛ nnoɔma no. Na wɔbɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ AWURADE fie daa daa Yehoiada berɛ so nyinaa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Yehoiada bɔɔ akora, na wanyini pa ara no, ɔwui. Na ɔwuiɛ no, na wadi mfirinhyia ɔha aduasa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wɔkɔsiee no Dawid kuro mu, ahemfo no nkyɛn, ɛfiri sɛ ɔdii asɛmpa Israel ne Onyankopɔn ne ne fie no ho.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Yehoiada wuo akyiri no, Yuda mmapɔmma ba bɛkotoo ɔhene no. Ɛnna ɔhene no tiee wɔn.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔgyaa AWURADE wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn fie, na wɔkɔsomm Asera nnua ne ahoni no. Na wɔn asodie yi nti abufuo baa Yuda ne Yerusalem so.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔsomaa adiyifoɔ maa wɔbaa wɔn mu sɛ wɔmmɛsane wɔn mmra AWURADE nkyɛn, na wɔdii wɔn adanseɛ, nanso wɔantie.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Nyankopɔn honhom baa Ɔsɔfoɔ Yehoiada ba Sakaria so, na ɔkɔgyinaa soro ɔman no anim ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ Onyankopɔn seɛ nie: Adɛn nti na moto AWURADE mmara nsɛm? Na ɛrensi mo yie. Sɛ moagya AWURADE yi, ɔno nso agya mo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔpam ne tiri so, na wɔkɔsii no aboɔ, sɛdeɛ ɔhene hyɛeɛ no AWURADE fie abannwa so.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Ɔhene Yoas ankae adɔeɛ a Sakaria agya Yehoiada de yɛɛ no no, na ɔkumm ne ba no. Na ɔrewuo no, ɔkaa sɛ: AWURADE nhwɛ na ɔntɔ so were.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na afe no awieeɛ no, Siriafoɔ dɔm tu baa ne so, na wɔbaa Yuda ne Yerusalem, na wɔbɛsɛee ɔman no mmapɔmma no nyinaa firii ɔman no mu, na wɔn asadeɛ no nyinaa, wɔde kɔmaa Damasko hene.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na nnipa kakraa bi na Siriafoɔ dɔm de baeɛ, nanso AWURADE de dɔm kɛseɛ pa ara hyɛɛ wɔn nsa, ɛfiri sɛ na wɔagya AWURADE wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no. Na Yoas nso, wɔne no dii atemmusɛm.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔfirii ne so sii mu kɔeɛ, na wɔgyaa no apirakuro bebree mu, na ne nkoa pamm ne tiri so, Ɔsɔfoɔ Yehoiada mma no mogya nti, na wɔkɔkumm no ne mpa so, na ɔwui. Na wɔsiee no Dawid kuro mu, nanso wɔansie no ahemfo no asieeɛ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na wɔn a wɔpamm ne tiri soɔ no nie: Sabad, Amonni baa Simeat ba ne Yehosabad, Moabni baa Simrit ba.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ne mma no ne ɛtoɔ dodoɔ a wɔgyee no no, ne Nyankopɔn fie asiesie no, hwɛ, wɔatwerɛ no Ahemfo Nwoma Nkyerɛaseɛ no mu. Na ne ba Amasia bɛdii n’adeɛ."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Amasia dii mfeɛ aduonu nnum na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfirinhyia aduonu nkron wɔ Yerusalem. Na ne na din de Yehoadan a ɔfiri Yerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ deɛ ɛtene AWURADE ani so, nanso ɛnyɛ n’akoma pɛyɛ mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ ahennie no timm ne nsam pɛ, ɔkunkumm ne nkoa a wɔkumm n’agya, ɔhene no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔn mma deɛ, wankum wɔn, sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no mmara no mu, Mose nwoma mu no a AWURADE hyɛɛ sɛ: Agyanom nnwu, mma nti, na mma nso nnwu, agyanom nti, na onipa no ara bɔne nti na wɔmma no nwuo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Amasia boaboaa Yuda ano hyiae, na wɔde wɔn gyinagyinae, mpanimfie so ne mpem mpem so asafohene, ne ɔha ha so asafohene so, Yuda ne Benyamin nyinaa mu, na ɔkanee wɔn firi wɔn a wɔadi mfeɛ aduonu ne akyire so. Na ɔhunuu wɔn sɛ wɔyɛ nnipa a wɔayi wɔn mpemahasa a wɔtumi ɔsatuo kura mpea ne akyɛm.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nanso ɔde dwetɛ dwetikɛseɛ ɔha kɔbɔɔ Israel mu nnipa mpemha a wɔyɛ mmarima a wɔtumi wɔn ho pa ara.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Nyankopɔn nipa bi baa ne nkyɛn bɛkaa sɛ: Ɔhene, mma Israel dɔm no ne wo nnkɔ, na AWURADE nni Israel, Efraim mma no nyinaa akyi;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> nanso sɛ wosusu sɛ woyɛ saa a na wobɛnya ɔko no mu ahoɔden a, Onyankopɔn bɛma woahwe ase wo tamfo anim; ɛfiri sɛ Onyankopɔn wɔ tumi sɛ ɔboa anaa ɔma obi hwe aseɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛnna Amasia bisaa Nyankopɔn nipa no sɛ: Na ɛdeɛn na yɛnyɛ dwetikɛseɛ ɔha a mede ama Israel asafo no? Na Nyankopɔn nipa no se: Ɛwɔ AWURADE nsam sɛ ɔbɛma wo adeɛ pii asene yei.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Amasia paee no asafo a wɔfiri Efraim baa ne nkyɛn no mu sɛ wɔnkɔ wɔn tenabea; na wɔn bo fuu Yuda sɛ, na wɔde abufuhyeɛ sane kɔɔ wɔn tenabea.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Amasia hyɛɛ ne ho den, na ɔde ne dɔm no kɔɔ Nkyene-Bonhwa no mu, na ɔkɔkum Seirfoɔ no mu nnipa mpemdu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔn mu nnipa mpemdu nso, Yudafoɔ no faa wɔn nnommum animono so, na wɔde wɔn kɔɔ ɔbotan bi atifi, na wɔtotoo wɔn firii ɔbotan no atifi hwehwee fam maa wɔn nyinaa mu paepaee.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na asafo a Amasia maa wɔsanee sɛ wɔne no nnkɔ ɔsa no mma kɔguu Yuda nkuro so, firi Samaria kɔduruu Bet-horon, na wɔkunkumm wɔn mu nnipa mpensa, na wɔfom adeɛ bebree fae.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Amasia firii Edomfoɔ kum sane baeɛ no, ɔde Seirfoɔ anyame bae, na ɔde bɛsisii hɔ fae sɛ anyame, na ɔkotoo wɔn anim, na ɔhyee aduhwam maa wɔn.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE abufuo sɔre tiaa Amasia, na ɔsomaa odiyifoɔ bi baa ne nkyɛn bɛbisaa no sɛ: Adɛn nti na woahwehwɛ ɔman bi anyame a wɔantumi annye wɔn man amfiri wo nsam no?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔrekasa akyerɛ no no, ɔhene ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Wɔahyɛ wo ɔhene fotufoɔ? Gyae! Adɛn nti na wɔnku woɔ? Na odiyifoɔ no gyaee, na ɔkaa sɛ: Mahunu sɛ AWURADE abɔ ne tirim sɛ ɔbɛsɛe wo, ɛfiri sɛ woayɛ yei, na woantie m’afotuo no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnna Yudahene Amasia tuu agyina, na ɔsomaa Israelhene Yoas a ɔyɛ Yehoahas ba Yehu baa ne nkyɛn sɛ: Bra ma yɛnsɔ yɛn ho nhwɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Israelhene Yoas soma maa wɔkɔɔ Yudahene Amasia nkyɛn sɛ: Nkasɛɛ dua a ɛwɔ Lebanon no soma maa wɔkɔɔ tweneduro a ɛwɔ Lebanon no nkyɛn sɛ: Fa wo ba ma me ba nware. Na wiram mmoa a wɔwɔ Lebanon no sene bɛtiatiaa nkasɛɛ dua no so.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Wose: Hwɛ, woakum Edom, na w’ahoahoa wo ho sɛ worehwehwɛ animuonyam. Afei tena wo fie. Adɛn nti na wo ne mmusuo rebɛdi aperepereɛ na woahwe aseɛ, wo ne Yuda nyinaa?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Amasia antie, ɛfiri sɛ Nyankopɔn nsam na ɛfire, sɛ ɔde wɔn bɛhyɛ obi nsam, sɛ wɔasom Edom anyame no nti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Israelhene Yoas foro bae, na wɔde bɛbɔɔ anim, ɔno ne Yudahene Amasia wɔ Bet-semes a ɛyɛ Yuda dea no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Yuda gui wɔ Israel anim, na wɔdwanedwane kɔɔ wɔn ntomadan mu.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Yudahene Amasia a ɔyɛ Yoas ba, Yehoahas ba deɛ, Israelhene Yoas kyeree no Bet-semes, na ɔde no baa Yerusalem na ɔdwirii Yerusalem fasuo no firii Efraim pono ho de kɔsii ntweaso pono no ho, basafa ahanu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔfaa sika ne dwetɛ nyinaa ne nnwinneɛ a wɔhunuu no Nyankopɔn fie, Obed-Edom nsam no nyinaa, ne ahemfie akoradeɛ no ne nnommum no nso, na ɔsane kɔɔ Samaria.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Yudahene Amasia a ɔyɛ Yoas ba dii mfirinhyia dunum, Israelhene Yoas a ɔyɛ Yehoahas ba no wuo akyi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Amasia ho nsɛm nkaeɛ, akane deɛ ne akyire yi deɛ no, hwɛ, wɔantwerɛ no Yuda ne Israel Ahemfo Nwoma no mu anaa?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɛfiri berɛ a Amasia sane firii AWURADE akyire no, wɔpamm ne tiri so wɔ Yerusalem, na ɔdwane kɔɔ Lakis, na wɔsoma maa wɔtii no kɔɔ Lakis kɔkumm no wɔ hɔ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wɔsoaa no apɔnkɔ so bae, na wɔbɛsiee no n’agyanom nkyɛn wɔ Dawid kuro no mu."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Yuda man no nyinaa faa Usia, na wadi mfirinhyia dunsia, na wɔsii no hene n’agya Amasia ananmu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɔno na ɔkyekyeree Elot, na ɔdane maa Yuda, akyire yi a ɔhene no tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Usia dii mfeɛ dunsia na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ aduonum mmienu wɔ Yerusalem. Na ne na din de Yekalia a ɔfiri Yerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ deɛ ɛtene AWURADE ani so, sɛdeɛ n’agya Amasia yɛeɛ no ara.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔhwehwɛɛ Onyankopɔn nna a Sakaria a ɔyɛ Nyankopɔn adehunu mu nhunumufoɔ no wɔ hɔ no nyinaa, na nna nso a ɔhwehwɛɛ AWURADE no, Onyankopɔn maa no dii yie.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔfirii adi ne Filistifoɔ kɔkoe, na ɔbubuu Gat fasuo ne Yabne fasuo ne Asdod fasuo, na ɔkyekyeree nkuro Asdod ho ne Filistifoɔ no mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Onyankopɔn boaa no tiaa Filistifoɔ ne Arabfoɔ a na wɔtete Gur-baal, ne Meunifoɔ no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Amonfoɔ de apeatoɔ brɛɛ Usia, na ne din hyeta kɔduruu Misraim, na ne ho yɛɛ den kɔɔ so pa ara.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Usia totoo aban atentene wɔ Yerusalem, ntweaso pono no so, ne bonhwa pono no so ne emu fam ntweaso no so, na ɔhyehyɛɛ no den.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔtotoo aban atentene nso ɛserɛ so, na ɔtutuu mmura pii, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔwɔ mmoakuo bebree mpaperɛ ne asaseta so. Ɔwɔ akuafoɔ ne bobeturoyɛfoɔ, mmepɔ so ne Karmel so, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔpɛ kua.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Usia wɔ dɔm a wɔdi ako a wɔtu sa asafo soɔ, sɛdeɛ wɔn nkaneeɛ a wɔnam Ɔtwerɛfoɔ Yeiel ne Ɔpanin Maaseia so kan wɔn no ano teɛ, wɔn nso na wɔhyɛ Hanania a ɔfiri ɔhene asafohene no mu no aseɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Agyanom atitire a wɔwɔ mmarima akofoɔ no mu no nyinaa ano si mpennu ahansia.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɛdɔm a ɛhyɛ wɔn aseɛ a wɔtumi wɔn ho ano si mpemahasa ne mpemnson ahanum, akofoɔ a wɔwɔ tumi ne ahoɔden de boa ɔhene tia atamfoɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Wɔn na Usia siesiee akyɛm, mpea, nnadeɛkyɛ, nkataboɔ, ntadua ne ntɔmmoɔ maa wɔn, sɛ wɔmfa mma dɔm no nyinaa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ adetoɔ mfidie a ɛyɛ adwumfoɔ adwini wɔ Yerusalem, sɛ ɛnsisi aban atentene so ne afasuo ntweaso, na wɔmfa ntoto agyan ne aboɔ akɛseɛ. Na ne din hyeta kɔɔ akyirikyiri pa ara, na ɔnyaa mmoa a ɛyɛ nwanwa kɔsii sɛ ne ho yɛɛ den.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ne ho yɛɛ den no, ɔyɛɛ ahantan na ɔbɔɔ brafunu, na ɔfomm AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn, na ɔhyɛnee AWURADE asɔredan mu sɛ ɔrekɔhye aduhwam aduhwamhyeɛbukyia no so.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Ɔsɔfoɔ Asaria dii n’akyi, na AWURADE asɔfoɔ aduɔwɔtwe, nnipa a wɔtumi wɔn ho ka ne ho.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔkɔgyinae ne Ɔhene Usia dii asie, na wɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Usia, ɛnyɛ wo deɛ sɛ wobɛhye aduhwam ama AWURADE, na ɛyɛ asɔfoɔ, Aaron mma a wɔayɛ wɔn kronkron sɛ wɔnhye aduhwam no dea. Firi adi firi kronkronbea ha yi, na woafom, na w’anim nyɛ nyam AWURADE Nyankopɔn anim.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Usia bo fui, na aduhwamhyeɛ adeɛ no kura ne nsam sɛ ɔde rebɛhye aduhwam no. Na ɔfaa asɔfoɔ no ho abufuo no, kwata fifirii ne moma so, asɔfoɔ no anim, AWURADE fie hɔ, aduhwamhyeɛbukyia no ho.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Ɔsɔfopanin Asaria danee n’ani kyerɛɛ no, ɔne asɔfoɔ no nyinaa, na hwɛ, wayare kwata ne moma so, na wɔpiapiaa no firii hɔ, na ɔno ara nso yɛɛ ntɛm firii adi, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE aka no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Ɔhene Usia yaree kwata kɔsii ne wuda, na ɔtenaa ayarefoɔ fie sɛ ɔkwatani, na wɔsii no AWURADE fie kwan. Na ne ba Yotam dii ɔhene fie no so, na ɔbuu asase no so man no atɛn.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Usia ho nsɛm nkaeɛ, akane deɛ ne akyire yi deɛ no, Amos ba Odiyifoɔ Yesaia atwerɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Usia tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando, na wɔsiee no n’agyanom nkyɛn ahemfo asieeɛ asase no so, na wɔkaa sɛ: Ɔyaree kwata. Na ne ba Yotam bɛdii n’adeɛ."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Yotam dii mfeɛ aduonu nnum na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ dunsia wɔ Yerusalem. Na ne na din de Yerusa a ɔyɛ Sadok ba.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ deɛ ɛtene AWURADE ani so, sɛdeɛ n’agya Usia yɛeɛ no ara. Nanso wanhyɛne AWURADE asɔredan no mu. Nanso ɔman no kɔɔ so bɔɔ ɔbra bɔne ara.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɔno na ɔsii AWURADE fie atifi pono no. Na Ofel fasuo no nso, ɔtoo bebree.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔkyekyeree nkuro nso wɔ Yuda mmepɔ so, na ɔtotoo aban a ɛyɛ den ne aban atentene kwaeɛ mu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔno ara na ɔne Amonfoɔ hene kɔkoeɛ, na ɔdii wɔn so tumi. Na Amonfoɔ no maa no dwetɛ dwetikɛseɛ ɔha ne ayuo kor mpemdu ne atokoɔ nso mpemdu afe no mu. Amonfoɔ no de nnoɔma bi brɛɛ no afe a ɛtɔ so mmienu ne mmiɛnsa mu nso.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Yotam yɛɛ ɔberempɔn, ɛfiri sɛ ɔsiesiee n’akwan AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn anim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Yotam ho nsɛm nkaeɛ ne n’akodie ne n’akwan nyinaa, hwɛ, wɔatwerɛ no Israel ne Yuda Ahemfo Nwoma no mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɔdii mfeɛ aduonu nnum na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ dunsia wɔ Yerusalem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Yotam tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando, na wɔsiee no Dawid kuro no mu. Na ne ba Ahas bɛdii n’adeɛ."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ahas dii mfeɛ aduonu na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ dunsia wɔ Yerusalem. Na wanyɛ deɛ ɛtene AWURADE ani so sɛ n’agya Dawid.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔnantee Israel ahemfo akwan so, na ɔyɛɛ guo ahoni nso maa Baalim.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔhyee aduhwam Hinom ba bonhwa no mu, na ɔhyee ne mma wɔ ogya mu, sɛdeɛ akyiwadeɛ a amanaman a AWURADE tutuu wɔn firii Israelfoɔ anim no yɛeɛ no teɛ no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔbobɔɔ afɔdeɛ na ɔhyee nnuhwam sorɔnsorɔmmea ne nkokoɔ so ne nnua frɔmfrɔm nyinaa ase.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn de no hyɛɛ Siriahene nsa, na wɔkaa no gui, na wɔfaa ne nnipa mu pii nnommum, na wɔde wɔn kɔɔ Damasko. Nanso ɔde no hyɛɛ Israel hene nsa, na ɔde okumkɛseɛ kaa no gui.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Remalia ba Peka kunkumm Yuda mu nnipa mpemha aduonu da koro, mmarima a wɔtumi wɔn ho ara nko, ɛnam sɛ wɔagya AWURADE wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn ntira.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Sikri, Efraim dɔmmarima bi, kumm ɔhene ba Maaseia ne ahemfie bapɔmma Asrikam ne Elkana a ɔdi ɔhene akyire.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no faa wɔn nuanom mu nnipa mpemahanu nnommum, mmaa, mmammarima ne mmammaa, na wɔfomm wɔn asadeɛ bebree fae, na wɔde asadeɛ no kɔɔ Samaria.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na AWURADE diyifoɔ bi wɔ hɔ a ne din de Oded. Ɔno na ɔfirii adi kɔhyiaa dɔm a wɔreba Samaria no, na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Hwɛ, AWURADE mo agyanom Nyankopɔn no abufuo a ɛsɔre tiaa Yuda no nti na ɔde wɔn ahyɛ mo nsa, na mode abohuro kɛseɛ akunkum wɔn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na afei, Yuda ne Yerusalem mma no na mose moredi wɔn nya ayɛ nkoa ne mfenaa yi? Mo deɛ, ɛnyɛ mo ara na ɛso deda mo soɔ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn anim?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na afei, montie me, na momma nnommum a mofaa wɔn firii mo nuanom mu no nsane nkɔ, na AWURADE abufuhyeɛ asɔre atia mo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnna Efraimfoɔ atitire mu binom, Yohanan ba Asaria, Mesilemot ba Berekia ne Salum ba Yehiskia ne Hadlai ba Amasa sɔresɔre tiaa wɔn a wɔfiri sa baeɛ no,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na wɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Mommfa nnommum no mma ha, ɛfiri sɛ mode deɛ ɛde AWURADE anim asodie bɛba de abɛpae yɛn bɔne ne yɛn asodie dada no soɔ, ɛfiri sɛ yɛn asodie dɔɔso ma yɛn, na AWURADE abufuhyeɛ wɔ Israel so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛnna wɔn a wɔamia no gyaa nnommum no ne asadeɛ no, asafohene no ne badwa no nyinaa anim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na mmarima a wɔabobɔ wɔn din no sɔresɔree, na wɔsosɔɔ nnommum no nsa, na wɔn mu wɔn a wɔdeda adagya no, wɔde asadeɛ no mu ntoma bi firafiraa wɔn, na wɔhyehyɛɛ wɔn ntadeɛ ne mpaboa, na wɔmaa wɔn aduane dii, ne nsuo nomee, na wɔsrasraa wɔn, na wɔde wɔn a wɔntumi nnanteɛ nyinaa tenatenaa mfunumu so, na wɔde wɔn baa Yeriko, mmɛ kuro no mu wɔn nuanom nkyɛn. Na wɔsane kɔɔ Samaria.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛberɛ no mu, Ɔhene Ahas soma maa wɔkɔɔ Asiria hene nkyɛn sɛ ɔmmɛboa no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ na Edomfoɔ no aba abɛkunkum Yudafoɔ bi na wɔafa binom nnommum.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Filistifoɔ nso abɛgu mpaperɛ so ne Yuda anafoɔ fam nkuro so, na wɔagye Bet-semes ne Ayalon ne Gederot ne Soko ne ɛho nkurowa ne Timna ne ɛho nkurowa ne Gimso ne ɛho nkurowa, na wɔtenatenaa hɔ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɛsiane sɛ Israelhene Ahas ayɛ Yuda mu bisibasaa, na wafom AWURADE nti, AWURADE brɛɛ Yuda ase.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Asiriahene Tilgat-pilneser baa ne so bɛhiahiaa ne ho, na wanhyɛ no den,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na Ahas kɔfaa AWURADE fie no ne ahemfie ne mmapɔmma no fie nnoɔma, na ɔde maa Asiriahene; nanso ammoa no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na n’ahohiahia berɛ mu no Ɔhene Ahas no ara kɔɔ so fomm AWURADE,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> na ɔbɔɔ afɔdeɛ maa Damasko anyame a wɔkaa no guiɛ no, na ɔkaa sɛ: Siria ahemfo no anyame na wɔboa wɔn nti, wɔn na mɛbɔ wɔn afɔdeɛ na wɔaboa me. Nso wɔn na wɔyeyɛɛ ɔno ne Israel nyinaa suntidua.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Ahas boaboaa Nyankopɔn fie nnwinneɛ ano, na ɔtwitwaa Nyankopɔn fie nnwinneɛ no mu, na ɔtotoo AWURADE fie apono no mu. Na ɔsisii afɔrebukyia Yerusalem ntwea nyinaa so.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ sorɔnsorɔmmea Yuda nkuro nyinaa mu, sɛ wɔnhye aduhwam mma anyame foforɔ, na ɔhuruu AWURADE n’agyanom Nyankopɔn no bo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ne ho nsɛm nkaeɛ ne n’akwan nyinaa, akane deɛ ne akyire yi deɛ no, hwɛ, wɔatwerɛ no Yuda ne Israel Ahemfo Nwoma no mu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na Ahas tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando, na wɔsiee no Yerusalem kuro no mu; na wɔamfa no ankɔ Israel ahemfo asieeɛ. Na ne ba Hesekia bɛdii n’adeɛ."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hesekia bɛdii hene no, na wadi mfeɛ aduonu nnum, na ɔdii hene mfirinhyia aduonu nkron wɔ Yerusalem. Na ne na din de Abia a ɛyɛ Sakaria ba.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ deɛ ɛtene AWURADE ani so sɛdeɛ n’agya Dawid yɛeɛ no ara.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɔno deɛ, n’ahennie afe a ɛdi kan no mu, bosome a ɛdi kan no so na ɔhinihinii AWURADE fie apono no, na ɔmiamiaa mu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔde asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ no baa mu, na ɔboaboaa wɔn ano apueeɛ mpraeɛ no so,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Lewifoɔ, montie, afei monyɛ mo ho kronkron, na monyɛ AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn fie kronkron, na monyiyi fi no mfiri kronkronbea hɔ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na yɛn agyanom fomee, na wɔyɛɛ AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn ani so bɔne, na wɔgyaa no, na wɔyii wɔn ani firii AWURADE tenabea no ho, na wɔde wɔn akyi kyerɛɛ no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nso wɔtoo ntwironowa no apono mu, na wɔdunnumm nkanea no, na wɔanhye aduhwam, na ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ nso wɔammɔ no kronkronbea hɔ amma Israel Nyankopɔn no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Enti na AWURADE abufuo baa Yuda ne Yerusalem soɔ, na ɔde wɔn yɛɛ ahoyeradeɛ ne ahodwirideɛ ne hwerɛmabɔ, sɛdeɛ mo ara mode mo ani hunu yi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na hwɛ, yɛn agyanom atotɔ afena ano, na yɛn mmammarima ne yɛn mmammaa ne yɛn yerenom nso, yei nti wɔafa wɔn nnommum kɔ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Afei ɛwɔ m’akoma mu, sɛ me ne AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn bɛpam, na n’abufuhyeɛ no afiri yɛn so akɔ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Me mma, afei monnyɛ aniha, na mo na AWURADE ayi mo sɛ monnyina n’anim nsom, na monyɛ no asomfoɔ ne aduhwamhyefoɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnna Lewifoɔ no sɔreeɛ, Amasai ba Mahat ne Asaria ba Yoel, wɔfiri Kohatfoɔ mma mu; ne Merari mma mu: Abdi ba Kis ne Yehalelel ba Asaria; ne Gersonfoɔ no mu: Sima ba Yoah ne Yoah ba Eden.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ne Elisafan mma mu, Simri ne Yeiel; ne Asaf mma mu, Sakaria ne Matania;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ne Heman mma mu: Yehiel ne Simei; ne Yedutun mma mu: Semaia ne Usiel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔboaboaa wɔn nuanom ano, na wɔyɛɛ wɔn ho kronkron, na wɔbaa sɛdeɛ ɔhene hyɛɛ no AWURADE nsɛm soɔ no, sɛ wɔrebɛpepa AWURADE fie no mu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na asɔfoɔ no hyɛnee AWURADE fie no mu sɛ wɔrekɔpepa mu, na wɔyiyii fi a wɔhunuu no AWURADE fie no mu no nyinaa de baa AWURADE fie abannwa no so, na Lewifoɔ no sesa firii hɔ, na wɔkɔto guu Kidron subonhwa no mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na bosome a ɛdi kan no da a ɛdi kan no na wɔfirii kronkronyɛ no aseɛ, na bosome no mu da a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no, wɔduruu AWURADE ntwironowa no ho, na wɔyɛɛ AWURADE fie no kronkron nnawɔtwe; na bosome a ɛdi kan, da a ɛtɔ so dunsia no wɔwiee,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ɛnna wɔhyɛnee mu baa Ɔhene Hesekia nkyɛn, na wɔkaa sɛ: Yɛapepa AWURADE fie hɔ nyinaa ne ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no ne ɛho adeɛ nyinaa, ne nsiesieeɛ pono no ne ɛho nnoɔma nyinaa ho;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na nnoɔma a Ɔhene Ahas di hene no, ɔto guiɛ wɔ ne mmarato mu no nyinaa nso, yɛasiesie na yɛadwira ho, na hwɛ, ɛwowɔ AWURADE afɔrebukyia no anim.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɛnna Ɔhene Hesekia tuaa nhema boaboaa kuro no mmapɔmma no ano, na ɔforo kɔɔ AWURADE fie.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔde anantwinini nson ne adwennini nson ne nnwammaa nson ne mpapo nson kɔbɔɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ maa ahennie no ne kronkronbea no ne Yuda. Na ɔka kyerɛɛ Aaron mma, asɔfoɔ no, sɛ wɔmmɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ wɔ AWURADE afɔrebukyia no so.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na wɔkunkumm anantwie no, na asɔfoɔ no sɔɔ mogya no, na wɔde petee afɔrebukyia no so, na wɔkunkumm adwennini no de wɔn mogya petee afɔrebukyia no so, na wɔkunkum nnwammaa no de wɔn mogya petee afɔrebukyia no so.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔde bɔne ho afɔdeɛ mpapo no baa ɔhene badwa no anim, na wɔde wɔn nsa guguu wɔn so.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na asɔfoɔ no kunkumm wɔn, na wɔde wɔn mogya no yɛɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ guu afɔrebukyia no ho sɛ wɔde repata ama Israel nyinaa. Na Israel nyinaa na ɔhene no kaa sɛ, ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no yɛ Israel nyinaa dea.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔde Lewifoɔ no gyinagyinaa AWURADE fie, na wɔkurakura nnawuro ne mmɛnta ne asankuten sɛdeɛ Dawid ne ɔhene no Ɔdehunufoɔ Gad ne Odiyifoɔ Natan hyɛeɛ no. Na AWURADE nam n’adiyifoɔ nsa so na ɔhyɛeɛ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Lewifoɔ no de Dawid nsankuo no gyinagyina hɔ, na asɔfoɔ no nso de ntotorobɛnto.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na Hesekia kaa sɛ wɔmmɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ afɔrebukyia no so. Na ɛberɛ a wɔfirii ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no bɔ aseɛ no, AWURADE dwom ne ntotorobɛntohyɛne nso firii aseɛ Israelhene Dawid dwontoɔ nnoɔma no so.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na badwa no nyinaa kotokotoe, na wɔtotoo nnwom na wɔhyenhyɛnee ntotorobɛnto no ara de kɔsii sɛ wɔwiee ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no bɔ.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na wɔwiee ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no bɔ no, ɔhene ne wɔn a na wɔka ne ho no nyinaa kotokoto sɔree.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na Ɔhene Hesekia ne asafohene no ka kyerɛɛ Lewifoɔ no sɛ wɔmfa Dawid ne Ɔdehunufoɔ Asaf nsɛm nyi AWURADE ayɛ. Na wɔde anigyeɛ yii no ayɛ, na wɔbobɔɔ wɔn mu ase sɔree.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na Hesekia kaa sɛ: Afei moadwira mo ho ama AWURADE, montwe mpini, na momfa okum afɔdeɛ ne aseda afɔdeɛ mmra AWURADE fie. Na badwa no de okum afɔdeɛ ne aseda afɔdeɛ bae, na obiara a ɔwɔ ayamyɛ akoma no de ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ bae.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ a badwa no de baeɛ no ano si anantwie aduɔson, adwennini ɔha, nnwammaa ahanu. Yei nyinaa wɔde bɔɔ AWURADE ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na akronkronneɛ no yɛ anantwie ahansia ne nnwan mpensa.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Nanso na asɔfoɔ no nnɔɔso nti, wɔn nko ara antumi anyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no nyinaa, enti wɔn nuanom Lewifoɔ no boaa wɔn kɔsii sɛ wɔwiee adwuma no ansa na asɔfoɔ no reyɛ wɔn ho kronkron. Na na Lewifoɔ no akoma tene sene asɔfoɔ no wɔn ho kronkronyɛ no mu.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Nanso ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ ho sradeɛ ne ahwiesa a ɛka ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no ho dɔɔso bebree. Sɛ wɔsiesiee AWURADE fie som no nie.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na Hesekia ne ɔman no nyinaa ani gyee sɛ Onyankopɔn asiesie ɔman no, ɛfiri sɛ ntɛm so na wɔyɛɛ adeɛ yi."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Hesekia soma maa wɔkɔɔ Israel ne Yuda nyinaa so, na ɔtwerɛɛ nwoma nso kɔmaa Efraim ne Manase, sɛ wɔmmra AWURADE fie wɔ Yerusalem, na wɔmmɛdi Twam mma AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔhene no ne ne mmapɔmma ne badwa no nyinaa atu agyina wɔ Yerusalem sɛ wɔbɛdi Twam bosome a ɛtɔ so mmienu no so. —",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na wɔantumi anni no berɛ no mu, ɛfiri sɛ na asɔfoɔ no nnya nyɛɛ wɔn ho kronkron mmaa no nnɔɔso, na ɔman no nso nnya mmoaa wɔn ano Yerusalem. —",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na nhyehyɛɛ no sɔɔ ɔhene ne badwa no nyinaa ani.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔhyɛɛ asɛm no so mmom sɛ wɔmpae no Israel nyinaa mu mfiri Beer-seba nkɔsi Dan, sɛ wɔmmra mmɛdi Twam mma AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn wɔ Yerusalem, ɛfiri sɛ na wɔmmɔɔ mu nnii no sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na awɛmfoɔ de nwoma a ɛfiri ɔhene ne ne mmapɔmma nsam no sii mu kɔ kɔkyinii Israel ne Yuda nyinaa mu, sɛdeɛ ɔhene mmara no teɛ, kaa sɛ: Israelfoɔ, monsane mmra AWURADE, Abraham, Isak ne Yakob Nyankopɔn nkyɛn, na ɔno nso asane aba wɔn a wɔafiri mu aka ama mo afiri Asiria ahemfo nsam no nkyɛn.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na monnyɛ sɛ mo agyanom ne mo nuanom a wɔfomm AWURADE wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn, na ɔde wɔn yɛɛ ɔsɛeɛ adeɛ, sɛdeɛ mo ara mohunu yi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Afei monnsensene mo kɔn sɛ mo agyanom, momfa mo ho mma AWURADE, na mommra ne kronkronbea a wayɛ no kronkron de rekɔsi daa no mu, na monsom AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn, na n’abufuhyeɛ no mfiri mo ho nkɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na sɛ mosane ba AWURADE nkyɛn a, mo nuanom ne mo mma bɛnya mmɔborɔhunu, wɔn a wɔfaa wɔn nnommum no nsam, na wɔasane aba asase yi so bio, na ɔdomfoɔ ne mmɔborɔhunufoɔ ne AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn, na sɛ mosane ba ne nkyɛn a, ɔrenyi n’ani mfiri mo so.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛnna asomafoɔ no sene firii kuro mu kɔɔ kuro mu, Efraim ne Manase asase so de kɔsii Sebulon tɔnn. Na wɔsereseree wɔn na wɔdii wɔn ho fɛw.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nanso ebinom a wɔfirii Aser ne Manase ne Sebulon brɛɛ wɔn ho ase na wɔbaa Yerusalem.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Nyankopɔn nsa baa Yuda nso so, sɛ ɔrema wɔn akoma korɔ sɛ wonni ɔhene ne asafohene no adeɛ a wɔde AWURADE asɛm hyɛeɛ no so.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na nkurɔfoɔ bebree boaa wɔn ano wɔ Yerusalem sɛ wɔrebɛdi apiti nnapɔnna no bosome a ɛtɔ so mmienu no so, badwa kɛseɛ pa ara.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔsɔre yiyii afɔrebukyia a ɛwowɔ Yerusalem no, na aduhwamhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no nyinaa nso wɔyiyii, na wɔkɔto guu asuwa Kidron mu.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ɛnna wɔkumm Twam Dwan no bosome a ɛtɔ so mmienu no da a ɛtɔ so dunan no. Na asɔfoɔ no ne Lewifoɔ no ani wui, na wɔdwiraa wɔn ho, na wɔde ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ baa AWURADE fie.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wɔkɔgyinagyinaa wɔn agyinaeɛ, sɛdeɛ wɔn amanneɛ no teɛ, Nyankopɔn nipa Mose mmara mu. Na asɔfoɔ no gyee mogya no Lewifoɔ no nsam de petee.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ na nnipa bebree wɔ badwa no mu a wɔnnya nyɛɛ wɔn ho kronkron, na Lewifoɔ no de Twam nnwan no kum ara maa wɔn a wɔn ho nteɛ no nyinaa, sɛ ɛnyɛ kronkron mma AWURADE.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔman no mu dodoɔ, nnipa bebree a wɔfiri Efraim ne Manase ne Isakar ne Sebulon annya annwira wɔn ho, na wɔdii Twam no, nso ɛnyɛ sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no. Ɛfiri sɛ Hesekia bɔɔ mpaeɛ maa wɔn, na ɔkaa sɛ: AWURADE a woyɛ, fa kyɛ",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> obiara a wasiesie n’akoma sɛ ɔrehwehwɛ Onyankopɔn, AWURADE n’agyanom Nyankopɔn, mpo sɛ ɛnyɛ kronkronbea ahodwira so a.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na AWURADE tiee Hesekia, na ɔsaa ɔman no yadeɛ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Israelfoɔ a wɔhunuu wɔn Yerusalem no dii apiti nnapɔnna no nnanson anigyeɛ kɛseɛ mu, na Lewifoɔ ne asɔfoɔ no de AWURADE nsankuo no yii AWURADE ayɛ nna nyinaa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Hesekia kaa Lewifoɔ a wɔwɔ AWURADE ho nimdeɛ pa no nyinaa abotɔyam asɛm, na wɔdii afahyɛ afɔrebɔdeɛ no nnanson, na wɔbobɔɔ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ, na wɔkamfoo AWURADE wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na badwa no nyinaa penee so, sɛ wɔbɛdi Twam no nnanson foforɔ nso, na wɔde anigyeɛ dii nnanson no bio.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Ɔhene Hesekia yii anantwinini apem ne nnwan mpemnson maa badwa no, na mmapɔmma no nso yii anantwie apem ne nnwan mpemdu maa badwa no. Na asɔfoɔ bebree dwiraa wɔn ho.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Yuda badwa no nyinaa ne asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ no, ne asafo a wɔfiri Israel baeɛ no nyinaa nso, ahɔhoɔ a wɔfiri Israel asase so baeɛ no ne wɔn a wɔte Yuda no ani gyee.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na anigyeɛ kɛseɛ baa Yerusalem; anigyeɛ a ɛfiri Dawid ba Salomo berɛ so ebi mmaa Yerusalem saa da.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ɛnna asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ no sɔreeɛ na wɔhyiraa ɔman no. Na wɔtee wɔn nne, na wɔn mpaebɔ duruu ne tenabea kronkron no ɔsoro."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wɔwiee yei nyinaa no, Israelfoɔ a wɔhunuu wɔn hɔ no nyinaa firii adi kɔɔ Yuda nkuro mu, na wɔkɔbubuu fadum, na wɔtwitwaa Asera nnua, na wɔdwirii sorɔnsorɔmmea ne afɔrebukyia no Yuda ne Benyamin nyinaa, ne deɛ ɛwɔ Efraim ne Manase no nso de kɔsii sɛ wɔwieeɛ. Ɛnna Israelfoɔ no nyinaa sane kɔɔ wɔn nkuro ne nkuraase.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Hesekia de asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ no nkyekyɛmu so atitire no sisii wɔn nkyekyɛmu so, obiara sɛdeɛ ne som teɛ, asɔfoɔ no ne Lewifoɔ no, sɛ wɔmmobɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ na wɔnsom na wɔnna ase, nyi ayɛ AWURADE nsraban apono mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na mmoa a ɛfiri ɔhene nnoɔma mu no, wɔde ma ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, anɔpa ne anwummerɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, ne home nna ne abosome foforɔ ne afahyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no, sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no AWURADE mmara mu no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔhyɛɛ nkurɔfoɔ a wɔte Yerusalem no sɛ wɔmfa asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ no kyɛfa mma, na wɔasɔ AWURADE mmara no mu den.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na asɛm no hyetae no, Israel mma no de ayuo ne nsa ne ngo ne ɛwoɔ ne mfuo mu nnɔbaeɛ nyinaa mu adikanneɛ bebree bae, na nnoɔma nyinaa mu ntotosoɔ du du no nso, wɔde pii bae.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Israel ne Yuda mma a wɔtete Yuda nkuro mu no, wɔn nso wɔde anantwie ne nnwan mu ntotosoɔ du du ne akronkronneɛ a wɔdwira wɔn ho ama AWURADE wɔn Nyankopɔn no mu ntotosoɔ du du bae, na wɔde bɛguu hɔ akuakuo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bosome a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no mu na wɔfirii akuakuo no aseɛ, na bosome a ɛtɔ so nson no mu na wɔwieeɛ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛnna Hesekia ne asafohene no ba bɛhunuu nnoɔma akuakuo no, wɔhyiraa AWURADE ne ne man Israel.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Hesekia bisaa asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ no akuakuo no ho asɛm.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛnna Asaria, ɔsɔfo panin a ɔfiri Sadok fie no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Ɛfiti sɛ wɔfirii aseɛ de mmasoɔ adeɛ baa AWURADE fie no, yɛadidi amee, ama pii aka, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE ahyira ne man, na nkaeɛ ne kuo kɛseɛ yi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Hesekia hyɛɛ sɛ wɔnsiesie mpumpunu AWURADE fie; na wɔsiesiee,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na wɔde mmasoɔ adeɛ no ne ntotosoɔ du du no ne akronkronneɛ no hyɛɛ hɔ nokorɛdie so. Na ɛso panin ne Lewini Kanania, na ne nua Simei di hɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Yehiel ne Asasia ne Nahat ne Asahel ne Yerimot ne Yosabad ne Eliel ne Ismakia ne Mahat ne Benaia ne ɛso hwɛfoɔ wɔ Kanania ne ne nua Simei ase, sɛdeɛ Ɔhene Hesekia ne Nyankopɔn fie so panin Asaria hyɛeɛ no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Imna ba Kore, Lewini a ɔwɛn apueeɛ pono no na na ɔhwɛ Nyankopɔn ayamyɛ ayɛyɛdeɛ no soɔ, sɛ ɔde AWURADE mmasoɔ adeɛ ne akronkronneɛ mu adekronkron no bɛma.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na n’ase na Eden ne Miniamin ne Yesua ne Semaia, Amaria ne Sekania hyɛ, wɔ asɔfoɔ nkuro no mu, de nokorɛdie kyɛ wɔn nuanom nnoɔma, sɛdeɛ nkyekyɛmu no teɛ, ɔkɛseɛ deɛ te sɛ akumaa deɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛsono wɔn a wɔkan wɔn sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusua teɛ deɛ a wɔde ma mmarima a wɔadi mfeɛ mmiɛnsa de rekorɔ, wɔn a wɔba AWURADE fie bɛyɛ wɔn adwuma sɛdeɛ da biara deɛ teɛ, sɛ wɔn nkyekyɛmu teɛ no;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ne asɔfoɔ no nkaneeɛ deɛ, sɛdeɛ wɔn mpanimfie teɛ, ne Lewifoɔ no deɛ nso, de firi deɛ wadi mfirinhyia aduonu so de rekorɔ, sɛdeɛ wɔn dibea teɛ wɔ wɔn akuo mu,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ne wɔn mma nkumaa ne wɔn yerenom ne wɔn mmammarima ne wɔn mmammaa nyinaa nkaneeɛ deɛ nso, sɛdeɛ asafo no nyinaa teɛ, ɛfiri sɛ wɔn nokorɛdie so na wɔyɛɛ akronkronneɛ no ho adeɛ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Aaron mma, asɔfoɔ no a wɔwɔ wɔn nkuro ho mmoa adidibea nsase so mfuo mu, mmarima a wɔabobɔ wɔn din mmaako mmaako wowɔ nkuro no nyinaa mu sɛ wɔmfa kyɛfa no mmema asɔfoɔ no mu mmarima nyinaa ne wɔn a wɔakan wɔn Lewifoɔ no mu no nyinaa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Hesekia yɛɛ saa ara Yuda nyinaa mu. Na ɔyɛɛ deɛ ɛyɛ, na ɛtene na ɛyɛ nokorɛ AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn anim.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na nneyɛɛ a ɔfirii aseɛ Nyankopɔn fie som mu ne mmara ne mmara nsɛm mu, de hwehwɛɛ ne Nyankopɔn no nyinaa, ɔde n’akoma nyinaa na ɛyɛeɛ, na ɛsii no yie."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Nsɛm yi ne nnwuma mu nokorɛdie yi akyiri no, Asiriahene Sanaherib bae, na ɔbaa Yuda so bɛkyeree nkuro a ɛyɛ den no ho nsraban, na ɔsusuu sɛ ɔbɛdwiri afa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Hesekia hunuu sɛ Sanaherib aba na n’ani wɔ so sɛ ɔne Yerusalem rebɛko no,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ɔne ne mmapɔmma ne n’atumfoɔ tuu agyina sɛ wɔbɛsisi nsuo aniwa a ɛwowɔ kuro no ho no; na wɔboaa no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na nkurɔfoɔ bebree bɛhyiae, na wɔsisii nsuo aniwa nyinaa ne asutene a ɛsene fa asase no soɔ, kaa sɛ: Adɛn nti na Asiriahene mmra mmɛnya nsuo a ɛdɔɔso?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔhyɛɛ ne ho den, na ɔtoo ɔfasuo a abubuo no nyinaa, na ɔmaa no korɔn kɔsii aban atentene no ho, na ɔtoo ɔfasuo foforɔ, kuro no akyi, na ɔhyɛɛ Milo a ɛwɔ Dawid kuro mu no den, na ɔyeyɛɛ akodeɛ ne akyɛm bebree.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔde ɔsa mu asafohene sisii ɔman no so, na ɔhyiaa wɔn baa ne nkyɛn, kuro pono ano mpraeɛ no so, na ɔkasa twaa wɔn bo too wɔn yam sɛ:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Monhyɛ mo ho den na mo ho nyɛ den, monnsuro na mo akoma nntu Asiriahene no ne n’asafo yuu a wɔka ne ho no anim, na deɛ ɔne yɛn wɔ hɔ no so sene deɛ ɛne no wɔ hɔ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɔno deɛ, honam nsa na ɛne no wɔ hɔ, na yɛn deɛ, AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn na ɔne yɛn wɔ hɔ, sɛ ɔbɛboa yɛn na wako yɛn ko ama yɛn. Ɛnna ɔman no de wɔn ho too Yudahene Hesekia nsɛm no soɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yei akyiri no, Asiriahene Sanaherib somaa ne nkoa maa wɔbaa Yerusalem, na ɔno deɛ, na ɔwɔ Lakis ho, na wɔn a na ɔdi wɔn soɔ nyinaa ka ne ho, ma wɔbɛka kyerɛɛ Yudahene Hesekia ne Yuda nyinaa a wɔwɔ Yerusalem no sɛ:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Sɛ Asiriahene Sanaherib seɛ nie: Mo a mote Yerusalem a wɔatwa ho ahyia, ɛdeɛn so na mo ani da?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnyɛ nnaadaa na Hesekia redaadaa mo, ama moabɛwu ɛkɔm ne sukɔm mu, reka sɛ: AWURADE yɛn Nyankopɔn bɛyi yɛn Asiriahene nsam no?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnyɛ ɔno Hesekia no ara na ɔyiyii ne sorɔnsorɔmmea ne n’afɔrebukyia no, na waka akyerɛ Yuda ne Yerusalem sɛ: Afɔrebukyia baako anim na monsɔre, na ɛso na monhye aduhwam no?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Monnya nhunuu deɛ me ne m’agyanom ayeyɛ nsase so amanaman nyinaa no? Nsase so amanaman no anyame atumi agye wɔn nsase no me nsam anaa?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Amanaman yi a m’agyanom asɛe wɔn pasapasa no anyame nyinaa mu hwan na watumi agye ne man me nsam, na mo nyame na ɔbɛtumi agye mo me nsam?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na afei mommma Hesekia nnsisi mo na ɔnnnaadaa mo saa, na monnnye no nnni, ɛfiri sɛ ɔman anaa ahennie biara nyame biara ntumi nnyee ne man me nsam anaa m’agyanom nsam, na nkantom mo nyame no; na ɔrennye mo me nsam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ne nkoa nso kaa deɛ ɛkyɛne yei tiaa AWURADE Nyankopɔn ne n’akoa Hesekia.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔtwerɛɛ nwoma nso de bɛbɔɔ AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no ahohora, kaa ne ho asɛm sɛ: Sɛ nsase so amanaman no anyame annye wɔn aman me nsam no, sɛ nso Hesekia nyame no renyi ne man me nsam ne no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔde nne kɛseɛ teaa mu Yuda kasa mu frɛɛ Yerusalem man a wɔwɔ ɔfasuo soɔ no, sɛ wɔreyi wɔn hu na wɔasuro binim na wɔanya kuro no afa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na wɔkasa tiaa Yerusalem Nyankopɔn no sɛ asase so amanaman anyame a wɔyɛ onipa nsa ano adwuma no.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Ɔhene Hesekia ne Amos ba Odiyifoɔ Yesaia bɔɔ yei ho mpaeɛ na wɔteaa mu kyerɛɛ ɔsoro.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE somaa ɔbɔfoɔ maa no bɛdwerɛɛ Asiriahene nsraban mu nnɔmmarima a wɔtumi wɔn ho ne mmapɔmma ne asafohene nyinaa, na ɔde aniwuo sane kɔɔ n’asase so. Na ɔkɔhyɛnee ne nyame fie, na ɛhɔ na wɔn a wɔfiri ne yafunu mu no mu bi maa no tɔɔ nkrantɛ ano.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Saa na AWURADE gyee Hesekia ne wɔn a wɔte Yerusalem no nkwa firii Asiriahene Sanaherib ne nnipa nyinaa nsam, na ɔmaa wɔn ho tɔɔ wɔn afa nyinaa hyiae.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na nnipa bebree de ayɛyɛdeɛ brɛɛ AWURADE wɔ Yerusalem, na wɔde aboɔdenneɛ brɛɛ Yudahene Hesekia, na wɔmaa no so amanaman nyinaa ani so, yeinom akyi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ɛberɛ no mu no Hesekia yaree owuyadeɛ; na ɔbɔɔ AWURADE mpaeɛ, na ɔbuaa no, na ɔmaa no nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ bi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nanso ɔyɛ maa no no, Hesekia anhyɛ no ananmu sɛdeɛ yie a ɔyɛ maa no no teɛ, na mmom n’akoma yɛɛ ahantan, na AWURADE abufuo baa ɔno ne Yuda ne Yerusalem so.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Hesekia sane brɛɛ ne ho ase n’akoma ahantan no ho, ɔno ne Yerusalemfoɔ nyinaa, enti AWURADE abufuo no amma wɔn so Hesekia berɛ so.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na Hesekia nyaa ne ho ne animuonyam pii, na ɔyɛɛ adekorabea maa dwetɛ ne sika ne abohene ne aduhwam ne akyɛm ne afɛfɛdeɛ nyinaa",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ne adekora adan maa ayuo ne nsa ne ngo nnɔbaeɛ, ne anantwie ahodoɔ nyinaa ne nnwan nso.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na ɔkyekyeree nkuro na ɔnyaa nnwan ne anantwie akuakuo bebree. Na Onyankopɔn maa no adeɛ bebree pa ara.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Saa Hesekia yi ara sii Gihon nsuo atifi nsuniwa no ano, na ɔde nsuo no nam mpumpunaseɛ baa Dawid kuro no atɔeɛ fam. Na Hesekia dii yie ne nneyɛɛ nyinaa mu.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na ne saa nti Babel mmapɔmma akyeame a wɔsomaa wɔn ne nkyɛn sɛ wɔmmɛbisa anwanwadeɛ a ɔyɛɛ no asase no soɔ no baeɛ no, Onyankopɔn gyaa no sɛ ɔresɔ no ahwɛ na wahunu n’akoma mu nyinaa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na Hesekia ho nsɛm nkaeɛ ne n’adɔeɛyɛ no, hwɛ, wɔatwerɛ no Amos ba Odiyifoɔ Yesaia adehunu mu, Yuda ne Israel Ahemfo Nwoma no mu.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na Hesekia tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando, na wɔsiee no Dawid mma asieeɛ deɛ ɛkorɔn, na Yuda ne Yerusalemfoɔ nyinaa dii no ni wɔ ne wuo mu. Na ne ba Manase bɛdii n’adeɛ."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Manase dii mfeɛ dummienu na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ aduonum nnum wɔ Yerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ AWURADE ani so bɔne sɛ amanaman a AWURADE tuu wɔn Israelfoɔ anim no.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔsane totoo sorɔnsorɔmmea a n’agya Hesekia bubuiɛ no, na ɔsisii afɔrebukyia maa Baalim, na ɔyɛɛ Asera nnua, na ɔsɔree ɔsoro asafo nyinaa na ɔsom wɔn.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔsisii afɔrebukyia AWURADE fie, sɛdeɛ AWURADE aka ho asɛm sɛ: Yerusalem na me din bɛtena akɔsi daa hɔ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔsisii afɔrebukyia memaa ɔsoro asafo nyinaa, AWURADE fie abannwa mmienu no so.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔde ne mma bɔɔ afɔdeɛ ogya mu Hinom ba bonhwa no mu, na ɔdii abayisɛm, bisaa adeɛ, yii ntafowa, na ɔyɛɛ asamanfrɛfoɔ ne adunsinfoɔ, na ɔyɛɛ AWURADE ani so bɔne bebree pa ara de huruu ne bo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔde ohoni a ɔseneeɛ no sii Nyankopɔn fie a Onyankopɔn ka kyerɛɛ Dawid ne ne ba Salomo sɛ: Efie yi ne Yerusalem na mafa afiri Israel mmusuakuo nyinaa mu, sɛ mede me din bɛsi hɔ akɔsi daa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na merenkɔ so mentwe Israel nan mfiri asase a mahyɛ ama wɔn agyanom no so: Hwɛ ara nko na wɔnhwɛ nyɛ adeɛ a mahyɛ wɔn no nyinaa, Mose nsa ano mmara ne ahyɛdeɛ ne atemmudeɛ nyinaa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Manase daadaa Yuda ne Yerusalemfoɔ maa wɔyɛɛ bɔne sene amanaman a AWURADE sɛee wɔn Israelfoɔ anim no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Manase ne ne man no, nanso wɔantie.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE maa Asiriahene asahene baa wɔn soɔ, na wɔde nkɔtɔkorɔ kyeree Manase, na wɔde kɔbere mfrafraeɛ mpokyerɛ guu no, na wɔde no kɔɔ Babel.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ne ho hiaa no no, ɔhwehwɛɛ AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn, na ɔbrɛɛ ne ho ase pii wɔ n’agyanom Nyankopɔn anim.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔbɔɔ no mpaeɛ no, AWURADE tiee ne nkotosrɛ, na ɔde no sane baa Yerusalem n’ahennie mu. Ɛnna Manase hunuu sɛ AWURADE ne Onyankopɔn.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na yei akyiri no, ɔtoo Dawid kuro akyi fasuo, Gihon atɔeɛ, subonhwa no mu de kɔsii Mpataa Pono ano, na ɔde twaa Ofel ho hyiae, na ɔmaa no korɔn yie. Na ɔde dɔm asafohene duaduaa Yuda nkuro a ɛyɛ den nyinaa mu.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔyii ananafoɔ anyame ne ahoni no firii AWURADE fie ne afɔrebukyia a ɔsisii no AWURADE fie bepɔ soɔ ne Yerusalem no nyinaa, na ɔkɔtoto guu kuro no akyi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔsii AWURADE afɔrebukyia no bio, na ɔbobɔɔ so asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ ne aseda afɔdeɛ, na ɔhyɛɛ Yuda sɛ wɔnsom AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nanso ɔman no kɔɔ so bɔɔ afɔdeɛ wɔ sorɔnsorɔmmea no so, nso na AWURADE wɔn Nyankopɔn nko na wɔbɔ ma no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Manase ho nsɛm nkaeɛ ne ne mpaeɛ a ɔbɔɔ ne Nyankopɔn ne adehunufoɔ a wɔde AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn din kasa kyerɛɛ no no nsɛm no, hwɛ, ɛwɔ Israel Ahemfo ho Nsɛm no mu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ne mpaebɔ ne sɛ wɔtiee no no, ne ne bɔne ne mmarato nyinaa, ne faako a ɔtotoo sorɔnsorɔmmea, na ɔsisii Asera nnua ne ahoni ansa na ɔrebrɛ ne ho aseɛ no, hwɛ, wɔatwerɛ no adehunufoɔ nsɛm mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Manase tii n’agyanom wɔ asamando, na wɔsiee no ne fie, na ne ba Amon bɛdii n’adeɛ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Amon dii mfeɛ aduonu mmienu na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ mmienu wɔ Yerusalem.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ AWURADE ani so bɔne sɛdeɛ n’agya Manase yɛeɛ no, na ahoni a n’agya Manase yɛeɛ no nyinaa, Amon bobɔɔ afɔdeɛ maa wɔn na ɔsomm wɔn.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wammrɛ ne ho ase AWURADE anim sɛdeɛ n’agya Manase brɛɛ ne ho aseɛ no, na ɔno Amon maa mfomsoɔ dɔɔso.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ne nkoa pamm ne tiri so kumm no ne fie.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na asase no sofoɔ no kunkumm Ɔhene Amon atirisopamfoɔ no nyinaa, na asase, no sofoɔ no de ne ba Yosia sii hene n’ananmu."
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Yosia dii mfeɛ nwɔtwe na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfirinhyia aduasa baako wɔ Yerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ deɛ ɛtene AWURADE ani so, na ɔnantee n’agya Dawid akwan so, na wammane ankɔ nifa anaa benkum.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na n’ahennie afe a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe so, a ɔda so yɛ abɔfra no, ɔfirii aseɛ hwehwɛɛ n’agya Dawid Nyankopɔn, na afe a ɛtɔ so dummienu soɔ no, ɔfirii aseɛ tee Yuda ne Yerusalem ho firii sorɔnsorɔmmea ne Asera nnua ne ɔsene ahoni ne eguo ahoni no ho.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔdwirii Baalim afɔrebukyia no n’anim, na owia adum a ɛsisi soɔ no, ɔtwitwa gui, na Asera nnua ne ɔsene ahoni ne eguo ahoni no, ɔbubui, na ɔsisirii, na ɔto petee wɔn a wɔbɔɔ afɔdeɛ maa wɔn no adamena so.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na asɔfoɔ no nnompe nso, ɔhyee no wɔn afɔrebukyia no so, na ɔtee Yuda ne Yerusalem ho.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ saa ara, Manase ne Efraim ne Simeon nkuro ne ɛho amamfo so de kɔsii Naftali.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔdwirii afɔrebukyia no, na Asera nnua ne ahoni no, ɔbubu sisirii, na owia adum no nyinaa ɔtwitwa gui, Israel asase nyinaa so. Na ɔsane baa Yerusalem.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na n’ahennie afe a ɛtɔ so dunwɔtwe so, a ɔwiee asase no ne efie no ho teɛ no, ɔsomaa Asalia ba Safan ne kuro no so safohene Maaseia ne Ɔkaefoɔ Yoahas ba Yoah sɛ wɔnkɔ nkɔmiamia AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn fie no mu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔbaa Ɔsɔfopanin Hilkia nkyɛn, na wɔde sika a wɔde aba AWURADE fie a Lewifoɔ apono ano ahwɛfoɔ no aboa ano afiri Manase ne Efraim ne Israel nkaeɛ nyinaa, ne Yuda ne Benyamin nyinaa, ne Yerusalemfoɔ nkyɛn no maa wɔn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔde hyɛɛ wɔn a wɔyɛ adwuma, a wɔayi wɔn asisi AWURADE fie no soɔ no nsa, na wɔn a wɔyɛ adwuma no, a wɔyɛ AWURADE fie adeɛ no de mae sɛ, wɔmfa nsiesie efie no na wɔmmiamia mu,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na wɔde maa nnua adwumfoɔ ne adansifoɔ, sɛ wɔmfa ntotɔ aboɔ a wɔatwa ne nnua mfa nyɛ mpuna ne nsamsoɔ nnua, adan a Yuda ahemfo asɛe no no mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na mmarima no yɛɛ adwuma no nokorɛdie mu. Wɔn so ahwɛfoɔ a wɔsisiiɛ no ne: Yohat ne Obadia, Lewifoɔ a wɔfiri Merari mma mu ne Sakaria ne Mesulam a wɔfiri Kohatfoɔ mma mu, sɛ wɔmpiapia adwuma no ne Lewifoɔ no mu wɔn a wɔnim dwontoɔ ho adeyɛ nyinaa;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na wɔdii nnesoasoafoɔ no so, na wɔhwɛɛ adwumayɛfoɔ nyinaa so sɛdeɛ ɔsom ahodoɔ no teɛ; nso na Lewifoɔ no mu binom yɛ atwerɛfoɔ ne mpanimfoɔ ne apono ano ahwɛfoɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔreyi sika a wɔde aba AWURADE fie no, Ɔsɔfoɔ Hilkia hunuu AWURADE mmara nwoma a ɔnam Mose so de maeɛ no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Hilkia bua see Ɔtwerɛfoɔ Safan sɛ: Mmara nwoma no na mahu no AWURADE fie yi. Na Hilkia de nwoma no maa Safan.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Safan de nwoma no brɛɛ ɔhene, nanso ɔde mmuaeɛ brɛɛ ɔhene sɛ: Adeɛ a wode ahyɛ wo nkoa nsa no nyinaa, wɔreyɛ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wɔhwiee sika a wɔhunuu no AWURADE fie no guu hɔ, na wɔde hyɛɛ ahwɛfoɔ no ne wɔn a wɔyɛ adwuma no nsa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Ɔtwerɛfoɔ Safan bɔɔ din kyerɛɛ ɔhene sɛ: Ɔsɔfoɔ Hilkia de nwoma bi ama me. Na Safan kenkanee mu wɔ ɔhene anim.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔhene tee mmara no mu nsɛm no no, ɔsunsuanee ne ntadeɛ mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɔhene hyɛɛ Hilkia, ne Safan ba Ahikam, ne Mika ba Abdon, ne Ɔtwerɛfoɔ Safan ne ahenkwaa Asaia sɛ:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Monkɔ nkɔbisa AWURADE hɔ adeɛ mma me ne Israel ne Yuda mu nkaeɛ, nwoma a wɔahunu no mu nsɛm no nti, na AWURADE abufuo a wɔahwie agu yɛn soɔ no so, sɛ yɛn agyanom anhwɛ AWURADE asɛm anyɛ no sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no nwoma yi mu nyinaa ho nti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛnna Hilkia ne wɔn a ɔhene somaa wɔn no kɔɔ Odiyifoɔbaa Hulda a ɔyɛ Hasra ba Tikwat ba Salum ntadehwɛfoɔ yere no nkyɛn. (Nso na ɔte Yerusalem kuro no nkyɛmu a ɛtɔ so mmienu no mu.) Na wɔkɔkaa saa kyerɛɛ no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no seɛ nie: Monkɔka nkyerɛ ɔbarima a ɔsomaa mo baa me nkyɛn no sɛ:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Sɛ AWURADE seɛ nie: Hwɛ, mede adebɔne bɛba ha yi ne ɛhafoɔ so, mede nnome a wɔatwerɛ no nwoma a wɔkenkan no Yuda hene anim no mu nyinaa bɛba,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ɛsiane sɛ wɔagya me na wɔakɔhye aduhwam ama anyame foforɔ, sɛ wɔde wɔn nsa ano nneyɛɛ nyinaa rehuru me bo, enti wɔbɛhwie m’abufuhyeɛ agu ha yi, na wɔrennum.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Yuda hene a ɔsomaa mo sɛ mommɛbisa AWURADE hɔ adeɛ no deɛ, sɛ monka nkyerɛ no nie: Sɛ AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn no seɛ nie: Nsɛm a woteeɛ no deɛ,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> sɛ w’akoma ayɛ bɛtɛbɛtɛ, na woabrɛ wo ho ase Nyankopɔn anim, ɛberɛ a wotee ne nsɛm, ɛha yi ne ɛhafoɔ ho, na woabrɛ wo ho ase m’anim asunsuane wo ntadeɛ mu, asu m’anim nti, me nso mate, AWURADE na ɔseɛ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hwɛ, wobɛto wo kɔn awu, na wɔasie wo wɔ da mu asomdwoeɛ mu, na adebɔne a mede mereba ha yi ne ɛhafoɔ soɔ no nyinaa deɛ w’ani renhunu. Na wɔde bɛbuaa ɔhene no.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ɛnna ɔhene no soma maa wɔkɔboaboaa Yuda ne Yerusalem mpanimfoɔ nyinaa ano hyiaeɛ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na ɔhene no foro kɔɔ AWURADE fie, na Yuda mmarima ne Yerusalemfoɔ nyinaa ka ne ho, ne asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ ne ɔman no nyinaa, ɛfiri ɔkɛseɛ so de kɔsi akumaa so, na ɔkenkanee apam nwoma a wɔhunuu no AWURADE fie no mu nsɛm nyinaa guu wɔn aso mu.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na ɔhene no kɔgyinaa ne gyinabea, na ɔyɛɛ apam AWURADE anim sɛ ɔbɛdi AWURADE akyi, na wahwɛ ne mmara nsɛm ne n’adansesɛm ne n’ahyɛdeɛ ayɛ afiri n’akoma nyinaa ne ne kra nyinaa mu, na wadi apam nsɛm a wɔatwerɛ no nwoma no mu no so.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na ɔmaa nnipa a wɔwɔ Yerusalem ne Benyamin gyinaa mu. Na Yerusalemfoɔ no yɛɛ sɛdeɛ Onyankopɔn, wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no apam no teɛ no.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na Yosia yiyii akyiwadeɛ no nyinaa firii nsase a ɛyɛ Israelfoɔ deɛ no nyinaa so, na ɔde wɔn a wɔwɔ Israel no nyinaa hyɛɛ ɔsom no mu maa wɔsom AWURADE wɔn Nyankopɔn. Ne nna nyinaa mu no, wɔamfiri AWURADE, wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no, akyiridie ho."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Yosia dii Twam Afahyɛ no wɔ Yerusalem maa AWURADE, na wɔkumm Twam dwan no bosome a ɛdi kan no, da a ɛtɔ so dunan no so.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔde asɔfoɔ no kɔsisii wɔn som adwuma so, na ɔhyɛɛ wɔn den maa AWURADE fie som no.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ Lewifoɔ a wɔkyerɛkyerɛ Israel nyinaa nhunumu na wɔyɛ akronkronfoɔ ma AWURADE no sɛ: Momfa adaka kronkron no mmɛsi efie a Israelhene Salomo, Dawid ba, siiɛ no mu. Morensoa no mo mmatiri so bio. Afei monsom AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn ne ne man Israel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na monsiesie mo ho, sɛ mo mpanimfie so, mo nkyekyɛmu mu, sɛdeɛ Israelhene Dawid ne ne ba Salomo twerɛeɛ no,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na monnyina kronkronbea sɛdeɛ mo nuanom, ɔman mma no mpanimfie nkyekyɛmu teɛ, na Lewifoɔ mpanimfie kyɛfa ntena hɔ mma obiara.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na monkum Twam dwan no, na monyɛ mo ho kronkron, na monsiesie mma mo nuanom, na monyɛ sɛdeɛ AWURADE nam Mose so kaeɛ no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Yosia yii nnwan nnwanten mma ne mmirekyie mma maa ɔman mma no, sɛ wɔmfa ne nyinaa nyeyɛ wɔn a wɔwɔ hɔ no nyinaa Twam afɔdeɛ, wɔn dodoɔ yɛ mpemaduasa ne anantwie nso mpensa. Yei nyinaa firi ɔhene akoradeɛ mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ne mmapɔmma nso yiyi maa ɔman no, asɔfoɔ ne Lewifoɔ no ayamyi so. Hilkia ne Sakaria ne Yehiel, Nyankopɔn fie mmapɔmma no de Twam nnwan mpennu ahansia ne anantwie ahasa maa asɔfoɔ no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Konania nso ne ne nuanom Semaia, Netanel, Hasabia, Yeiel ne Yosabad, Lewifoɔ asafohene no yii Twam nnwan mpemnum ne anantwie ahanum maa Lewifoɔ no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛnna wɔsiesiee ɔsom no, na asɔfoɔ no gyinagyinaa wɔn agyinaeɛ, na Lewifoɔ no nso wowɔ wɔn nkyekyɛmu mu, sɛdeɛ ɔhene hyɛeɛ no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na wɔkunkumm Twam nnwan no, na asɔfoɔ no de wɔn mogya no bi petee, na Lewifoɔ no dwaa wɔn.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔyii ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no sɛ wɔde rema ɔman mma no mpanimfie nkyekyɛmu no, sɛ wɔmfa nkɔma AWURADE sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no Mose nwoma mu no, ne anantwie no nso saa ara.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔde ogya totoo Twam dwan no sɛdeɛ amammerɛ teɛ. Na akronkronneɛ no deɛ, wɔnoaa no nkukuo ne nnadesɛn ne kyeɛ dadeɛ mu, na wɔde maa ɔman mma no nyinaa ntɛm so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Yei akyiri no, wɔsiesiee wɔn deɛ ne asɔfoɔ no deɛ, ɛfiri sɛ asɔfoɔ, Aaron mma no wɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no bɔ ne sradeɛ no hyeɛ ho ara de kɔsii adesaeɛ. Enti Lewifoɔ no siesiee wɔn ara wɔn deɛ ne asɔfoɔ, Aaron mma no deɛ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na nnwontofoɔ, Asaf mma no nso wɔ wɔn gyinabea, sɛdeɛ Dawid, Asaf, Heman ne Yedutun, ɔhene adehunufoɔ no hyɛeɛ no, na apono ano ahwɛfoɔ no wɔ ɛpono ne ɛpono ho: Na ɛnhia sɛ wɔgya wɔn som, ɛfiri sɛ wɔn nuanom Lewifoɔ siesie maa wɔn.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wɔsiesiee AWURADE som nyinaa da no, na wɔdii Twam no bobɔɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ AWURADE afɔrebukyia no so, sɛdeɛ Ɔhene Yosia hyɛeɛ no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Israelfoɔ a wɔhunuu wɔn hɔ no dii Twam no berɛ no mu, ne apiti nnapɔnna no nnanson.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɛfiri Odiyifoɔ Samuel berɛ soɔ no, na wɔnnii Twam bi sɛ yei wɔ Israel, na Israel ahemfo nyinaa nso anni bi a ɛte sɛ Twam a Yosia, asɔfoɔ, Lewifoɔ, Yuda nyinaa ne Israel a wɔwɔ hɔ no ne Yerusalemfoɔ diiɛ no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Yosia ahennie afe a ɛtɔ so dunwɔtwe so na wɔdii Twam yi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Yeinom nyinaa akyiri a Yosia asiesie efie no, Misraimhene Neko foro bae, na ɔbɛdii ako wɔ Karkemis, Eufrate ano. Na Yosia firii adi kɔhyiaa no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔsomaa abɔfoɔ baa ne nkyɛn sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na me ne wo, Yuda hene, wɔ yɛ? Ɛnyɛ wo so na mebaa nnɛ, na mmom efie a ɛne me di ako no so na Onyankopɔn aka sɛ menyɛ ntɛm. Ɛne Onyankopɔn a ɔka me ho no nnni asie, na wansɛe wo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nanso Yosia annane n’ani amfiri ne ho, na mmom ɔsakyeraa ne ho sɛ ɔne no rekɔko, na wantie Neko nsɛm a ɛfiri Nyankopɔn anomu no. Na ɔkɔ kɔkoe Megido bonhwa mu.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na agyantofoɔ toto sesaa Ɔhene Yosia, na ɔhene no ka kyerɛɛ ne nkoa sɛ: Momfa me mfiri ha nkɔ, na mapira sɛ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ne nkoa no yii no firii ne teaseɛnam no mu de no kɔɔ ne teaseɛnam a ɛdi hɔ no mu, na wɔde no baa Yerusalem. Na ɔwui, na wɔsiee no n’agyanom asieeɛ. Na Yuda ne Yerusalem nyinaa gyamm Yosia.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Yeremia twaa Yosia ho kwadwom, na nnwontofoɔ mmarima ne mmaa nyinaa bɔɔ Yosia din wɔn Kwadwom mu de bɛsi nnɛ, na wɔde yɛɛ ahyɛdeɛ Israel mu, na hwɛ, wɔatwerɛ no Kwadwom no mu.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Yosia ho nsɛm nkaeɛ ne n’adɔeɛyɛ, sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no AWURADE mmara mu",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ne ne ho nsɛm, akane ne akyire yi deɛ no, hwɛ, wɔatwerɛ no Israel ne Yuda Ahemfo Nwoma no mu."
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na asase no sofoɔ no faa Yosia ba Yehoahas sii no hene n’agya ananmu Yerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Yehoahas dii mfeɛ aduonu mmiɛnsa na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene abosome mmiɛnsa wɔ Yerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Misraimhene no tuu no adeɛ so Yerusalem, na ɔgyee asase no apeatoɔ dwetɛ dwetikɛseɛ ɔha ne sika dwetikɛseɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Misraimhene no de ne nua Eliakim sii Yuda ne Yerusalem so hene, na ɔdanee ne din yɛɛ no Yehoiakim; na ne nua Yehoahas deɛ, Neko faa no kɔɔ Misraim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Yehoiakim dii mfeɛ aduonu nnum na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ dubaako wɔ Yerusalem. Na ɔyɛɛ AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn ani so bɔne.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɔno so na Babelhene Nebukadnessar foro baeɛ, na ɔde kɔbere mfrafraeɛ mpokyerɛ guu no, sɛ ɔde no rekɔ Babel.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na AWURADE fie nnoɔma no bi nso Nebukadnessar de kɔɔ Babel kɔsiee n’ahemfie wɔ Babel.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Yehoiakim ho nsɛm nkaeɛ ne n’akyiwadeɛ a ɔyɛeɛ, ne deɛ wɔhunuu no ne ho no, hwɛ, wɔatwerɛ no Israel ne Yuda Ahemfo Nwoma no mu. Na ne ba Yehoiakyin bɛdii n’adeɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yehoiakyin dii mfeɛ nwɔtwe na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene abosome mmiɛnsa ne dadu wɔ Yerusalem. Na ɔyɛɛ AWURADE ani so bɔne.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na afe no duruiɛ no, Ɔhene Nebukadnessar soma maa wɔbɛfaa no ne AWURADE fie afɛfɛdeɛ nso kɔɔ Babel, na ɔde ne nua Sedekia sii Yuda ne Yerusalem so hene.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Sedekia dii mfeɛ aduonu baako na ɔbɛdii hene, na ɔdii hene mfeɛ dubaako Yerusalem.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn ani so bɔne. Wammrɛ ne ho ase Odiyifoɔ Yeremia a na ɔkasa AWURADE ano no anim.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Afei nso ɔtee Ɔhene Nebukadnessar a ɔmaa no kaa Nyankopɔn ntam no anim atua. Na ɔsenee ne kɔn na ɔpirim n’akoma sɛ ɔrensane mma AWURADE Israel Nyankopɔn nkyɛn.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nso asɔfoɔ no mu mpanimfoɔ nyinaa ne ɔman no maa wɔn mmarato dɔɔso pii sɛ wiase amanaman akyiwadeɛ nyinaa, na wɔguu AWURADE fie a wayɛ no kronkron Yerusalem no ho fi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na AWURADE wɔn agyanom Nyankopɔn no somaa n’abɔfoɔ baa wɔn nkyɛn, ɔtuaa nhema somaa wɔn, ɛfiri sɛ ne yam hyehyee no maa ne man ne ne tenabea no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nanso wɔdii Nyankopɔn abɔfoɔ no ho fɛw, na wɔbuu ne nsɛm no animtia, na wɔsereseree n’adiyifoɔ no de kɔsii sɛ AWURADE abufuhyeɛ no sɔre tiaa ne man no a wɔannya ano aduro.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔyii Kaldeafoɔ hene no baa wɔn so, na ɔde nkrantɛ bɛkunkumm wɔn mmeranteɛ, wɔ wɔn kronkronbea fie, na wanni aberanteɛ ne ababaa, akɔkoraa ne deɛ wafu dwono ho adɔna, ɔde wɔn nyinaa hyɛɛ wɔn nsa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Nyankopɔn fie nnoɔma no nyinaa, akɛseɛ ne nketewa, ne AWURADE fie akoradeɛ ne ɔhene no ne ne mmapɔmma akoradeɛ, ɔde ne nyinaa kɔɔ Babel.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na wɔhyee Nyankopɔn fie no, na wɔdwirii Yerusalem fasuo no, na emu aban afɛfɛ nyinaa, wɔde ogya hyee, na emu afɛfɛdeɛ nyinaa sɛee.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na nkaeɛ a wɔantotɔ afena ano no, ɔtuu wɔn kɔɔ Babel na wɔkɔyɛɛ ɔno ne ne mma nkoa kɔsii Persia ahennie no kyekyerɛ,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> sɛ wɔmma AWURADE asɛm a ɔde Yeremia ano kaeɛ no mmra mu, sɛ ɛnkɔsi sɛ asase no ani bɛsɔ ne home mfeɛ no; amamfo nna nyinaa na ɛrehome akɔsi sɛ mfirinhyia aduɔson bɛwie duro.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Persiahene Kores afe a ɛdi kan mu no, sɛ AWURADE asɛm a ɔde Yeremia ano kaeɛ no bɛba mu nti, AWURADE kanyann Persiahene Kores honhom, na ɔmaa wɔkɔpaee no n’ahennie nyinaa mu, na wɔtwerɛe nso sɛ:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Sɛ Persiahene Kores seɛ nie: Asase so ahennie nyinaa na AWURADE, ɔsoro Nyankopɔn no de ahyɛ me nsa, na ɔno ara de ato me so sɛ mensi efie memma no Yerusalem a ɛwɔ Yuda. Mo mu biara a ɔwɔ ha a ɔbɛtumi no, AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn nni n’akyi, na ɔmforo nkɔ."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;